Ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'ubwandu bushya bwa coronavirus (COVID-19) mu muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, hagati y'itariki ya 1 Mutarama n'iya 15 Werurwe 2020
Umubare w'abanduye indwara iterwa na koronavirusi (COVID-19) ugaragaza ko hari ihinduka nk'iryo mu bihugu byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, ibyo bikaba byemeza ko nubwo bari mu byiciro bitandukanye, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kigenda gihita mu bihugu byose.
Nk'uko byanagenze mu Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi barembye cyane bigomba kwitegura kwiyongera kw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho, cyane cyane mu byumba bita ku barembye.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, havuzwe ko habonetse icyorezo cy'indwara y'umwijima y'inkomoko idasanzwe i Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'u Bushinwa cyo Kurwanya no Gukumira Indwara cyatangaje ko icyateye iki cyorezo ari coronavirus nshya ubu izwi ku izina rya SARS-CoV-2.
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 yitwa indwara iterwa na koronavirusi (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, abagera kuri 80% by'abafite COVID-19 bafite uburwayi budafite ingufu, ni ukuvuga ubwandu bw'ibihaha bufite cyangwa budafite umusonga, abenshi muri bo bakira.
Hafi ya 14% by'abarwaye COVID-19 ni bo bayirwaye cyane bigasaba kuvurirwa mu bitaro, mu gihe 6% basigaye ni bo bayirwaye cyane bigasaba kwitabwaho cyane.
Imfu z'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bajyanywe mu bitaro zigera kuri 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, turagenzura uko ubwandu bwa COVID-19 buhuriye mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) na UK, maze tukagereranya n'uko byifashe mu Ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Turagereranya kandi umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA na UK mu gihe cya vuba n'uw'Ubutaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 yakomeje gukwirakwira, kandi uko icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje gukwirakwira hirya no hino ku isi, ubu ni ko bimeze muri iki gihugu.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, umuyobozi mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu igazeti ya Eurosurveillance yo ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, Spiteri et al. batangaje ko ari ubwa mbere abantu bemejwe ko banduye COVID-19 i Burayi nk'uko bisobanurwa na OMS.
Mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA, abantu batatu ba mbere byemejwe ko banduye babonetse mu Bufaransa ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bari bavuye Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari baramaze kugaragara muri buri gihugu mu bihugu 30 bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Afurika y'Uburayi na Ubwongereza (UK), aho kugeza ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 hari hamaze kwandura abantu 39 768 n'abapfuye 1,727 muri bo 17 750 n'abapfuye 1,441 bari baraguye mu Butaliyani gusa.
Kubara umubare w'abarwaye COVID-19 no kubara umubare w'abanduye
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no kurwanya indwara (ECDC), gitanga imibare y'abantu banduye COVID-19 muri buri gihugu ku isi, ivuye ku masoko yemewe nk'ibiro by'ubuzima, inzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu n'iz'akarere n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima, igashyirwa ku murongo buri munsi saa munani.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma uko COVID-19 yagiye igenda muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, no kugereranya n'ibyabaye mu Butaliyani.
Mu rwego rwo gusuzuma umubare w'abandura COVID-19, twabakiriye umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu gihe cy'iminsi 14, dufata ingamba z'uko COVID-19 igenda mu buryo bwa kamere mu bihugu byose bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, mu gihe cy'ukwezi kwa mbere kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Twagereranyije kandi umubare w'abanduye w'ibyabonywe muri buri gihugu guhera saa 8:00 za mu gitondo ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020 n'amakuru yo mu Butaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Uko COVID-19 yifashe mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza yakurikije cyane iyavuye mu ntara ya Hubei yo mu Bushinwa (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Ibihugu by'i Burayi na Areefa n'u Bwongereza, ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwatangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku ya 21 Gashyantare, hanyuma buzamuka cyane ahagana ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (amakuru y'inyongera).
Iki cyerekezo ahanini cyatewe n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'umubare w'abatangajwe ko banduye mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose byo muri EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza na byo byagize ubwiyongere nk'ubwo mu mibare y'abarwaye COVID-19 (amakuru y'inyongera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK ugereranyije n'amakuru y'Ubutaliyani yo kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Byagaragaye ko ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa 8:00, ibindi bihugu 15 bya EU/EEAG n'u Bwongereza byari bimaze gutanga amakuru angana cyangwa ari make ku mubare w'abanduye ugereranyije n'uwa Italiya mu byumweru 3 gusa bishize.
Ibisubizo byacu byerekana ko umubare w'abantu babonetse banduye COVID-19 wiyongera vuba muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Uko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wagiye utera imbere bigaragaza ko icyorezo cyateye imbere ku muvuduko ungana mu bihugu byose.
Ibyo ni ko biri nubwo ibihugu biri mu byiciro bitandukanye by'ibipimo kandi hakaba hari itandukaniro mu bisubizo by'inzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu, impinduka zishobora kuba mu bisobanuro by'abarwaye n'itandukaniro mu buryo bwo gutoranya abarwayi bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo bagaragaze ko banduye COVID-19, harimo no gupimwa kugira ngo basubire ku murongo.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere twibasiwe n'icyorezo mu Butaliyani bavuze ko abagera kuri 10% by'abarwaye COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, kandi itangazamakuru ryavuze ko ibitaro n'ibyumba by'indembe muri utwo turere byari bimaze kugera ku rwego rwuzuye.
Imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 batashyizwe mu bitaro no/cyangwa aho bavurirwa mu byumba by'indembe, ubu iboneka mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA ku rugero rwa 6% na 1% by'abanduye gusa (ntabwo byerekanywe).
Ariko kandi, hakenewe gukusanya amakuru ku buryo buhoraho kugira ngo hahuzwe amakuru y'ubugenzuzi agendanye n'umubare w'abamaze kwandura n'abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010/11 bwagaragaje itandukaniro rikomeye ry'umubare w'ibitanda biboneka mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bwo hagati n'ubuvuzi bwihariye mu Burayi, kuva ku bitanda 29,2 ku bantu 100 000 mu Budage kugeza ku bitanda 4,2 muri Porutugali.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bifite amikoro menshi cyangwa make ugereranyije n'Ubutaliyani (12.5 mu bitaro by'indembe n'ibitaramo ku bantu 100.000 mu 2010).
Imigaragarire yo kugenzura ibisabwa ku bijyanye n'ubwandu, hamwe n'ingengo y'imari ya buri gihugu cyo muri EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza ku bijyanye n'ubwandu bw'abarwaye COVID-19 bari mu bitaro bafite ibyago byo kurenza 90% by'ibitanda byo mu cyumba cy'indembe, byatanzwe mu mpinduka ya gatandatu y'igiteranyo cya COVID-19 cya CEPCM.
Kubera ko kugeza ubu abantu barembye mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibigo by'indembe bikunze kwakira abaturage bo mu karere runaka, amakuru yerekeye abantu barembye n'ibitanda byo mu cyumba cy'indembe yagombye gushyirwa ku rwego rwa 2 rw'ibarura ry'imibare (NUTS 2).
Ibyaranze Ubutaliyani n'ibibera mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo by'indembe bigomba kwitegura guhangana n'ubwandu bushya bwa SARS-CoV-2 mu baturage no kwitegura ko umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho, cyane cyane mu byumba by'indembe, nk'uko bimeze mu turere twugarijwe n'iki cyorezo mu Butaliyani.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe n'igenzura ry'ibyago ryihuta rya CEPCM riherutse gukorwa, uburyo bwihuse, bufatika kandi bwuzuye ni ingenzi mu kugabanya ikwirakwizwa rya SARS-COV-2, kuva ku buryo bwo gukumira ukagera ku buryo bwo kugabanya ubwandu, kubera ko kwiyongera k'umubare w'abandura vuba kandi hakiri kare bishobora gutuma abafata ibyemezo n'ibitaro badahabwa umwanya uhagije wo gusobanukirwa, kwemera no guhuza ibisubizo byabo, mu gihe nta kintu cyari cyakozwe mbere.
Igenzura ryihuse ry'ibyago ryerekana kandi ingamba z'ubuzima rusange zishobora kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Hari igihe gito buri gihugu gishobora gukoresha mu kongera ingufu mu kurwanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya umutwaro ku nzego z'ubuzima.
Bitabaye ibyo, birashoboka ko mu minsi cyangwa ibyumweru biri imbere, gahunda z'ubuzima zo mu bindi bihugu bigize EU/EEA zizaba zigomba guhangana n'umubare munini w'abarwayi bakeneye ubuvuzi bwihariye.
Icyorezo cya Koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe n'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (SARS) iterwa na Koronavirusi 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kugeza ubu kimaze guhitana abarenga 3000 no kwandura abarenga 80.000 mu Bushinwa no hirya no hino ku isi, bikaba byarabaye amakuba ku bantu.
Kimwe n'indi virusi ya SARS-CoV, yateje abantu ibihumbi na ibihumbi banduye SARS mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba yandura binyuze ku ducurama kandi igateza ibimenyetso nk'ibyo binyuze mu buryo nk'ubwo.
Ariko kandi, COVID-19 ifite ubukana n'ubukana buciriritse ugereranyije na SARS, ariko yandura cyane, kandi yibasira abantu bakuze kurusha abakiri bato, abagabo kurusha abagore.
Mu rwego rwo gusubiza umubare w'ibitabo by'ubuvuzi byiyongera ku buryo bwihuse kuri iyi ndwara igenda igaragara, iki kiganiro gishaka gutanga isesengura ryihariye kandi ryihariye kuri iki kibazo cy'ubushakashatsi bugenda bwiyongera.
Tuzaganira ku by'ibanze by'indwara, indwara, virusi, gusuzuma, kuvura, kuboneza no kwirinda indwara.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bigomba gusubizwa, twizera ko ibyo tugiye gusuzuma bizatuma turushaho gusobanukirwa neza iby'iyo ndwara iteye ubwoba, kandi bigatuma tuyisimbuka burundu.
Umunsi mukuru w'Icyicyi wo ku ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye uw'ingenzi ku Bushinwa, kubera ko abantu bari bamaze igihe kirekire mu kato mu gihe cy'Icyumweru cya Zahabu ndetse no mu bindi byumweru byinshi bitewe n'ikwirakwira ry'indwara nshya ya virusi.
Iyi virusi isa cyane na coronavirus (CoV) yateje icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero idasanzwe (SARS) mu 2003, niyo mpamvu ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020 Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (WHO) ryayise SARS-CoV-2, naho indwara ifitanye isano nayo yitwa Coronavirus disease 19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye i Wuhan, cyihuta gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa bwose, mbere yo gukwira mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi yari imaze gutuma abantu barenga 80.000 bandura COVID-19, abarenga 40.000 bakaba baragiye mu bitaro naho abarenga 3.000 bahasiga ubuzima.
OMS ivuga ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi w'abaturage wa mbere", ishobora kuba iteje akaga gakomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko byatangajwe na PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu mezi atageze kuri abiri, hasohotse inyandiko zirenga 200 ku byerekeye COVID-19, harimo izijyanye na virusi, indwara, isuzuma n'uburyo bwo kuyivura, kuva ku itariki ya 7 Mutarama 2020 ubwo habonekaga bwa mbere amakuru y'uburyo virusi yagaragaye mu barwayi benshi.
Iyi nyigo igerageza guhuza ubushakashatsi bwakozwe kuri iki kibazo gishya cyiyongera.
Tugiye kugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara ya koronavirusi, indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS, icyorezo cyabayeho mu 2012).
Tuzagaruka kandi ku byo twamenye kugeza ubu mu bijyanye no kwirinda no gupima indwara, ndetse no gukemura ibibazo bimwe na bimwe bikiri mu nzira ariko byihutirwa.
Ubusanzwe, koronavirusi zafashwe nk'indwara zitangiza abantu, zigatera hafi 15% by'indwara zisanzwe zo mu mutwe 4.
Nyamara muri iki kinyejana, twabonye koronavirusi ebyiri zishobora gutera indwara cyane ku bantu, ari zo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatangiye gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa mu 2003 no muri Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, zigasatira vuba mu bindi bihugu byinshi, zigatuma abantu barwara kandi bagapfa cyane.
Iki cyorezo cya COVID-19 ni icya gatatu cya coronavirus cyibasiye isi mu bihe bya vuba.
Nk'uko bigaragazwa ku ishusho ya 1.1, icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ibicurane icyo gihe kitari kizwi cyatangiye kuvugwa i Wuhan ku wa 31 Ukuboza 2019 mu Nteko y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima mu Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, amakuru agaragaza uko virusi ya korona igenda ikurikirana yaramenyekanye.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, umuntu wa mbere wahitanywe n'icyorezo cy'isura y'umuntu muri Wuhan.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyari cyarakwirakwiriye mu buryo bwihuse mu mijyi, intara no mu bihugu by'abaturanyi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, havugwa ko abakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima banduye, byerekana ko abantu bashobora kwandura.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan washyizwe mu kato, kandi imodoka zose zitwara abantu zikaba zarahagaritswe.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe ku ndwara bwerekanye ko mu barwayi 41 bemejwe, 21 gusa ari bo bahuye n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Wuhan, aho bivugwa ko ubwandu bwatangiriye ku nyamaswa zitazwi.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo cyugarije isi.
Mu gihe iyi raporo yandikwa, iyi ndwara yari imaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa bwose no mu bindi bihugu hafi 50 ku isi hose (Igishushanyo (Igishushanyo cya 2).
Kubera ko ibintu bigenda bihinduka vuba, ntiharamenyekana neza ubukana n'ubukana bw'icyorezo.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu bigo byinshi ku barwayi 8,866, barimo 4,021 byemejwe ko barwaye COVID-19, bwagaragaje amakuru agezweho y'icyorezo (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 yanduye abantu bari mu kigero cy'imyaka yose, ariko cyane cyane mu kigero cy'imyaka 30-65.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri (47,7%) cy'abanduye bari bafite imyaka irenga 50, bake cyane bari munsi y'imyaka 20, naho 14 gusa bari munsi y'imyaka 10.
SARS-CoV-2 yanduza cyane abagabo (0.31 kuri 100 000) kurusha abagore (0.27 kuri 100 000).
COVID-19 yagaragaye mu turere, cyane cyane mu ntara ya Hubei no mu nkengero zayo.
Ikigereranyo cy'igihe hagati y'intangiriro y'ibimenyetso n'isuzuma rya COVID-19 cyari iminsi 5 (2-9).
Igihe cyo gutwita cyari iminsi 4.8 (3,0-7,2).
Igihe cyo hagati yo kugaragara n'urupfu cyari iminsi 9.5 (4,8-13).
Igipimo cy'ubwinshi (R0) cyari 3.77 (IC ku 95%: 3.51 - 4.05) naho R0 y'ibanze yari 2.23 - 4.82.
Umubare w'abanduye wariyongereye cyane kugeza ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020, ubwo habagaho ingendo nyinshi mbere y'umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi mu Bushinwa.
Umubare w'abapfuye mu barwayi bagaragaye ko ari abemejwe ko banduye wari 1.44% (IC 95%: 1.10-1.86%), naho umubare w'abapfuye mu barwayi bose wari 3.06% (IC 95%: 2.02-4.59%).
Ibintu bitatu by'ibanze byavuzwe ko bitera COVID-19 ni igitsina (abagabo), imyaka (≥60) n'indwara ikomeye y'ibihaha.
Coronavirusi ni umuryango muto w'udukoko tw'udupfukamunwa twinshi dukozwe na RNA imwe.
Zishobora kugabanywamo ubwoko bune, ari bwo alpha, beta, gamma na delta, koronavirusi zizwi ko zanduza abantu ziri mu bwoko bwa alpha na beta.
Igisate cy'umugozi cyitwa Spike (S) gifatana n'indwara ya SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, mu buryo bukurikira, cyitwa angiotensin converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) na dipeptidyl peptidase-4 (DPP4) mu misemburo yacyo yo mu ngirabuzima, hanyuma habaho guhuza imiterere y'uruhu.
Ingirabuzimafatizo ya virusi ya RNA irekurwa muri cytoplasm; nyuma yo kwigana ingirabuzimafatizo ya virusi, ingirabuzimafatizo ya RNA iherekejwe na glycoproteins z'umwenda na poroteyine za nucleocapside zubaka uduseke turimo virusi, noneho tugahuriza hamwe n'uruhu rwa plasma kugira ngo dukure virusi.
Ku ya 10 Mutarama 2020, hatangajwe ku nshuro ya mbere uko genom ya SARS-CoV-2 iteye.
SARS-CoV-2 yagaragajwe ko ari ubwoko bushya bwa betacoronavirus, ifite ibipimo birenga 99.98% by'imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo mu bipimo 10 byafashwe aho icyorezo cyatangiriye, ku isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Huanan mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
SARS-CoV-2 ifite imiterere ya jenome isa cyane na SARS-CoV kurusha MERS-CoV.
Hakoreshejwe porogaramu ya mikorosikopi ikoresha amashanyarazi, SARS-CoV-2 yagaragaye mu bice bito cyane by'ibice by'umubiri w'umuntu mu nzira z'ubuhumekero.
Abantu bafite LACE2 basuzumwe basanga ari bo bakira SARS-CoV-2 na SARS-CoV.
Icyakora poroteyine ya S yo muri SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano n'umuntu bita ACE2 ku rugero ruto ugereranyije n'iyo muri SARS-CoV, ibyo bikaba bihuye n'uko SARS-CoV-2 itatera ubwandu ku kigero cyo hasi ugereranyije na SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no gukora poroteyine ngufi nshya ikorwa na lorf3b ndetse n'iyororoka ikorwa na lorf8.
Lorf3b yo muri SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugira uruhare mu gutera indwara kwa virusi no kubuza kugaragaza lIFNβ; ariko, lorf8 nta bice cyangwa imiterere izwi ikora.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Zhou, et al., bagaragaje imiterere ya cryo-ME ya ACE2 yuzuye ya muntu ku cyemezo cya 2,9 Å mu kigo hamwe na transporter ya amino acide B0AT1.
Basanze iyo nganda ifite imiterere yafunze n'iyafunguye, ikaba ari inganda z'imiterere ibiri, kandi iyo nganda ACE2-B0AT1 ishobora guhuza poroteyine ebyiri za S, ibyo bikaba byatanga ibimenyetso byo kumenya no kwandura coronavirus.
B0AT1 ishobora kuba umuti ushobora gukoreshwa mu gupima imiti igamije kuvura SARS-CoV-2.
Umutware w'inkomoko n'umuyobozi w'intera
Byagaragaye ko SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zavuye mu nguge kandi ko zageze ku bantu zinyuze mu nguge no mu ngona.
Nyuma yo kugereranya imiterere ya SARS-CoV-2 n'izindi koronavirusi, havuzwe ko SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse ku ducurama kuko virusi nshya ihuriye ku kigero cya 96% na koronavirusi ebyiri zo mu bwoko bwa SARS zaturutse ku ducurama zitwa bat-SL-CoVZX45 na bat-SL-CoVZX21.
Ariko, umuyoboro wa mbere watumye virusi inyura mu moko y'inyamaswa ngo yandure abantu ntiwamenyekana, kandi inzira yo kwandura iracyari iyo gushakishwa.
Ji n'abandi batanze igitekerezo cy'uko virusi ishobora kuba yaturutse ku ducurama ikagera ku bantu ikoresheje inzoka, ibyo bikaba byumvikanisha ko hari aho ihuriye n'izindi muri poroteyine ya S.
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abashakashatsi bo muri Guangzhou, mu Bushinwa, pangolin - inyamaswa ifite umunwa muremure irya inkuruni, ikoreshwa cyane mu buvuzi gakondo bw'Abashinwa - ishobora kuba ari yo SARS-CoV-2 ifataho urugero, bitewe n'uko 99 ku ijana by'imiterere yayo ihuriye n'iya koronavirusi yavumbuwe muri pangolin na SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko, itandukaniro rya 1 ku ijana hagati ya jenome ebyiri ni itandukaniro rikomeye; ni yo mpamvu hakwiriye gutegerezwa ibisubizo byemeza by'ibimenyetso bifatika (Ig. (Ig.33)).
Imikorere ya SARS-CoV-2 mu buryo bw'imiterere n'imikorere byayo iracyari ingume.
SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zishobora kumara mu mubiri amasaha 48 ahantu humye, zikamara iminsi 5 mu bushyuhe bwa dogere 20 na humidite iri hagati ya 40 na 50%.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba ifite imiterere nk'iyo.
SARS-CoV-2 isa n'iyandura cyane kubera ko ishobora kwihanganira urumuri rw'izuba ndetse n'ubushyuhe bwa dogere 56C mu gihe cy'iminota 30, ether, 75% ethanol, umuti wica udukoko wa chlorine, peracetic acid, chloroform n'ibindi binyabutabire birimo ibinure ariko bitari chlorhexidine, bishobora guhagarika virusi.
Muri rusange, abantu bose nta bushobozi bafite bwo kwirinda SARS-CoV-2 bityo bakaba bashobora kuyandura.
Kugeza ubu, nta bushakashatsi bwimbitse bwakozwe ku bijyanye n'ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri ku ndwara ya SARS-CoV-2.
Ni yo mpamvu, dushobora kwifashisha gusa ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mbere kuri virusi zindi za koronavirusi, cyane cyane SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV (Igishushanyo (Igishushanyo cya 4).4).
Ubusanzwe, iyo virusi yanduje umuntu, ubusanzwe abarwayi ba mbere bamenya ko ari virusi binyuze mu buryo bw'umubiri bwo kwirinda indwara, bakamenya ko ari virusi binyuze mu buryo bw'umubiri bwo kumenya imiterere y'imiterere y'umubiri (PRR), harimo ubwoko bwa C bw'indwara y'indwara ya lectine, ubwoko bwa Toll (TLR), ubwoko bwa NOD (NLR) n'ubwoko bwa RIG-I (RLR).
Binyuze mu nzira zitandukanye, virusi ituma haboneka udukoko dutera indwara, ingirabuzimafatizo zikura kandi zikabyara interferon yo mu bwoko bwa I (IFN) igabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi kandi ikongera umuvuduko w'imikorere ya virusi.
Ariko, poroteyine N ya SARS-CoV ishobora gutuma virusi itinda ku mikorere y'umubiri.
Bidatinze, ubwirinzi bw'umubiri buza kwifatanya mu kurwanya virusi.
Insoro zitwa lymphocyte T, cyane cyane CD4+ na CD8+ T, zigira uruhare runini mu kurinda umubiri.
CD4+ T ziteza imbere ingirabuzimafatizo B zikora abasirikare barwanya virusi, naho CD8+ T ziteza imbere ingirabuzimafatizo zikora ubwandu.
Ingirabuzimafatizo za T zituma haboneka cytokine z'uburwayi zituma ubwirakabiri bugabanuka kugira ngo zite ku nzego z'ubwirinzi.
Icyakora, coronavirus ishobora kubuza ingirabuzimafatizo za T gukora binyuze mu gutuma zitakaza ubushobozi bwo gukora.
Ubwirinzi bwo mu bwonko, bufite ibipimo bya C3a na C5a hamwe n'abasirikare, na bwo ni ingenzi mu kurwanya ubwandu bw'agakoko gatera virusi.
Urugero, abasirikare b'umubiri b'umuntu wakize bashoboye guhashya MERS-CoV.
Ku rundi ruhande, iyo umubiri w'umuntu urenze urugero, utangira gukora ibintu bituma habaho umwotsi w'ibintu byangiza umubiri, bikaba byakwangiza cyane ibihaha n'izindi ngingo, kandi mu mimerere mibi cyane, bikaba byatuma umubiri utera indwara nyinshi, ndetse n'urupfu rukabaho.
Abantu bafite ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bakunze kugaragara mu bantu bakuru bafite uburwayi buzwi cyane n'abagore batwite.
Abantu benshi bemera ko abantu bagerwaho n'indwara nyinshi cyangwa bafite ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri bugabanutse cyane bashobora kwandura kurusha abandi.
Hagati y'iminsi 1 na 14 ni yo SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kumara, ariko muri rusange ni hagati y'iminsi 3 na 7 dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi 425 ba mbere bagaragaye i Wuhan.
Ariko, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi 1,099 bwerekanye ko igihe cyo kubyara cyari iminsi 3 ku kigereranyo, mu gihe cy'iminsi 0 kugeza kuri 24.
Ubushakashatsi bushya bwakozwe, nk'uko byasobanuwe haruguru, bwavuze ko igihe cyo kurama ari iminsi 4.8 (3,0-7,2) hakurikijwe umubare w'abantu 8 866.
Ni ngombwa cyane ko inzego z'ubuzima zihindura igihe nyacyo cyo kuguma mu kato zikagendera ku gihe cyo gutangira kwanduza gishobora kuba cyumvikana neza, kugira ngo abantu banduye ariko batagaragaza ibimenyetso by'indwara batandurira abandi virusi.
Ubusanzwe, abantu bagaragaweho cyangwa bandujwe na virusi bashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14.
Ese gahunda ya guma mu rugo igomba kongerwaho iminsi 24?
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 akenshi kiba ari cyo kimenyetso cya mbere kandi gikomeye, kandi gishobora kuba giherekejwe cyangwa kitagendana n'ibindi bimenyetso nk'inkorora, guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu myanya y'umubiri, kugira igisebe, kuribwa umutwe, kubabara mu muhogo, guhumeka, kubabara mu gatuza, kuruka, kugira isesemi no kuruka.
Bamwe mu barwayi bagaragaje impumuro mbi na/ cyangwa se impumuro nkeya mu maraso mu gihe cy'icyumweru kimwe nyuma y'uko barwaye.
Mu barwayi bafite ibibazo bikomeye, mu gihe gito cyane, haje indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero, guhumeka nabi, asidi yo mu mubiri n'indwara y'amaraso.
Abarwayi bafite umuriro n'/ cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka, ndetse n'abafite umuriro mwinshi, n'ubwo nta bimenyetso by'indwara biboneka mu mashusho y'ibipimo by'imiterere y'umutima, bagomba gupimwa virusi kugira ngo bashobore gusuzumwa hakiri kare.
Ubushakashatsi ku baturage bwakozwe mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019 bwagaragaje ko 98% by'abarwayi bari bafite umuriro, 76% bari bafite inkorora, 55% bari bafite ikibazo cyo guhumeka, 3% bari bafite ikibazo cy'isukari; 8% by'abarwayi bari bakeneye guhumeka.
Ibisubizo nk'ibyo byatanzwe n'ubushakashatsi bubiri buherutse gukorwa ku miryango n'icyorezo cy'ubwandu byatewe n'ubwandu bwa virusi buturutse ku muntu udafite ibimenyetso.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2012 ku bantu b'ibihe byose, bwagaragaje ko ibimenyetso by'ingenzi by'abarwaye MERS-CoV ari umuriro (98%), inkorora yumye (47%) na impumuro (55%).
Nyamara, 80% by'abarwayi bakeneye guhumeka, ni ukuvuga abarwayi benshi kurusha abafite COVID-19, ibyo bikaba bihuye n'umubare munini w'abahitanywe na MERS ugereranyije na COVID-19.
Indwara y'umuhogo (26%) n'iy'umuhogo (21%) nabyo byaravuzwe mu barwayi ba MERS.
Ku bijyanye na SARS, ibimenyetso by'ibanze byigaragaza ni umuriro (99%-100%), inkorora y'uruhu (29%-75%), umunaniro (40%-42%), isuka (20%-25%) no kuribwa mu muhogo (13%-25%), kandi abagera kuri 14-20% by'abarwayi bari bakeneye guhumeka.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Gashyantare, ubwandu bw'icyorezo cya COVID-19 bwari ku kigero cya 2%, ku isi hose hakaba hari abantu 66,576 banduye.
Mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo, mu kwezi k'Ugushyingo 2002 igipimo cy'abapfuye bishwe na SARS cyari 10% ku barwayi 8 096 bari bamaze kwemezwa ko banduye.
Ku barwayi ba MERS, hakurikijwe ubushakashatsi bwakozwe muri Kamena 2012, impfu zari 37% ku barwayi 2 494 bemejwe.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwagaragaje ko R0 ya SARS-CoV-2 yari 6.47 ku gipimo cy'ibyizere (IC) cya 95% cya 5.71-7.23, mu gihe R0 ya SARS-CoV yari hagati ya 2 na 4.
Gushushanya ibimenyetso, ubukana n'ingaruka za SARS-CoV-2, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV byerekanwa mu Gicumbi Gicumbi1.1.
Ibipimo tumaze kubona byerekana ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubushobozi bwo gukwirakwira cyane kurusha MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV, ariko ikaba idashobora kwica cyane.
Ni yo mpamvu, gukemura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 bigoye cyane kurusha uko byari bimeze ku cyorezo cya MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV.
Akenshi, ibyerekanwa ry'urwobo riba mu muryango cyangwa mu iteraniro cyangwa mu modoka, nk'uko bigenda ku rugendo rwo mu nyanja.
Abarwayi bakunze kuba baragiye cyangwa barigeze kuba i Wuhan cyangwa ahandi hantu habonetse indwara, cyangwa bakaba barigeze guhura n'abanduye cyangwa abarwayi mu byumweru bibiri bya mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira.
Icyakora, byagaragaye ko abantu bashobora gutwara virusi ariko ntibagaragaze ibimenyetso mu gihe kirenga ibyumweru bibiri, kandi ko abakize bashobora kongera gutwara virusi, ibyo bikaba byerekana ko hakenewe kongera igihe cyo gushyira abantu mu kato.
Abarwayi bafite umubare w'ingirabuzimafatizo zera z'amaraso (cyane cyane imirasire y'amaraso) zisanzwe cyangwa nkeya mu cyiciro cya mbere.
Urugero, indwara ya lymphocyte ifata ingirabuzimafatizo zera za &lt; 4 × 109/L na lymphocyte ifata &lt; 1 × 109/L, hamwe n'indwara ya aspartate aminotransferase na viremia byagaragaye mu barwayi 1,099 bafite COVID-19.
Bamwe mu barwayi bari bafite amaraso afite ibyitwa myoglobin, impyiko na poroteyine z'umwijima, kandi abenshi bari bafite poroteyine ya C- réactif na za erythrocyte sedimentation.
Mu barwaye indwara ikomeye, urugero rwa D-dimer, ni ukuvuga ikintu kiva mu kuvangura kwa fibrine mu maraso, rwaragutse, kandi umubare w'utugingo tw'umubiri w'amaraso y'amaraso uragenda ugabanuka.
Abantu benshi bafite COVID-19 bagaragaza uduhanga tw'ibimenyetso bidasanzwe mu kwitegereza ibipimo bya X-ray, bigaragazwa n'amafoto y'ibicu by'amaboko abiri cyangwa ibirahuri by'amababa.
Abarwayi bakunze kugira umusonga udasanzwe, uburwayi bukomeye bw'ibihaha n'indwara yo guhumeka nabi cyane (ARDS).
Iyo umuntu afite SDRA, guturika kudahita, amazi menshi no kugenda yiyongera, bituma umwuka utambuka nabi.
Kudakora neza kw'udutsi two mu myatsi twitwa type I na type II bituma havuka igipimo cyo hasi cy'ibintu bitanga umwanda no kwiyongera k'umuvuduko w'umurindi, bityo bikagabanya ubushobozi bw'ibihaha bwo kwipfundika, bityo bikaba byongera ibyago byo gufatwa n'ibihaha.
Ni yo mpamvu ibizamini by'umutima biba biteye ubwoba cyane akenshi biba mu gihe umuntu arwaye cyane.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, isesengura rya mbere ryakozwe ku ndwara ya COVID-19 ryagaragaje ko habonetse udutsi tw'utugingo tw'ibihaha, udutsi tw'uruhu, udutsi tw'udutsi tw'amaraso tw'imbere mu mubiri, n'udutsi tw'amaraso tw'ingengabuzima mu bihaha by'umurwayi wapfuye, ibyo bikaba bihuye n'uburwayi bw'ubwandu bwa virusi na SARS-CoV kandi bikaba bisa n'ibya SARS na MERS.
Gupima SARS-CoV-2 ikoresheje RT-PCR (reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction) byakoreshejwe nk'uburyo bw'ibanze bwo gupima COVID-19.
Ariko, kubera umubare munini w'ibisubizo by'ibinyoma, bishobora gutuma icyorezo cyihuta, ibimenyetso byo kwa muganga byatangiye gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma indwara (ntibikiri gushingira ku cyiciro cya RT-PCR) mu Bushinwa ku ya 13 Gashyantare 2020.
Ibintu nk'ibyo byari byaravuzwe mu gusuzuma SARS.
Bityo, guhuza amateka y'ubuzima bw'umuntu, ibimenyetso by'indwara, ibizamini byo muri laboratwari n'ibizamini bya radiyoloji ni ingenzi kandi ni ngombwa mu gusuzuma indwara neza.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda rya Zhang Feng ryasobanuye uburyo bwo gukoresha uburyo bwa SHERLOCK bushingiye ku ikoranabuhanga rya CRISPR mu gupima SARS-CoV-2, bushobora kugaragaza uduce twa RNA twakozwe na SARS-CoV-2 turi hagati ya 20 × 10-18 mol/L na 200 × 10-18 mol/L (10-100 kopi kuri microlitro y'ikigereranyo) hakoreshejwe agapapuro k'ibisubizo mu gihe kitarenze isaha, bidasabye ibikoresho bihambaye.
Twakwizera ko ubu buryo bushya buzatuma habaho iterambere rikomeye mu bijyanye n'ubushobozi n'imikorere, mu gihe byaba ngombwa ko bukoreshwa mu bizamini byo kwa muganga.
Kubera ko nta bumenyi bafite ku cyorezo cya koronavirusi, abaganga bashobora gusa gutanga ubufasha ku barwaye COVID-19, mu gihe bagerageza imiti itandukanye yakoreshejwe cyangwa yateguwe mu kuvura izindi koronavirusi, nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, ndetse n'izindi ndwara z'ibyorezo (Imbonerahamwe (Imbonerahamwe2).2).
Ubu buryo bwo kuvura burimo uburyo bwa none n'ubwo buzaboneka bwo kuvura hakoreshejwe imiti irwanya virusi, imiti igabanya ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri, imiti ya steroide, plasma y'abarwayi bakize, ubuvuzi bw'igishinwa ndetse n'ubufasha bw'imitekerereze.
Ndetse na plasma y'abantu barwaye ariko bakira, yagiye itangwa mu rwego rwo kubafasha.
Ibigo by'imiti byose birimo gukora ibishoboka byose kugira ngo haboneke abashobora kurwanya uwo mugera no kuwurwanya.
SARS-CoV-2 mu gutangira yibasira cyane cyane ibihaha, ariko ishobora no kwibasira mu rugero ruto ibindi bice byerekana ACE2, nk'urwungano ngogozi n'impyiko.
Nyamara, kudakora neza no guhumeka nabi ni byo bibangamiye abarwayi cyane kandi bikaba ari byo bituma abantu bapfa.
Bityo rero, ubufasha bwo guhumeka ni ingenzi mu kugabanya ibimenyetso no kurokora ubuzima; harimo oksijeni rusange, oksijeni yo mu rwego rwo hejuru, guhumeka bidasabye ubufasha no guhumeka nk'imashini, bitewe n'uburemere bw'indwara.
Abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso bikomeye byo guhumeka bagomba guhabwa umwuka wa oxygène uturuka mu mubiri (OMEC), uburyo bushya bwo guhumeka bw'umutima bukoreshwa mu kuvura ibibazo bikomeye by'umutima cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Ikindi kandi, kwita ku rugero rwiza rw'ibinyabuzima, kwirinda no kuvura indwara z'inyongera no kwanduza, no kurinda ingingo z'ingenzi, ni ingenzi ku barwayi ba SARS-CoV-2.
Byagaragaye ko igihe umubiri w'umuntu witabira cyane, bituma abarwayi ba SARS na MERS bagira ikibazo cy'imikorere y'umubiri.
Igitutu cy'ubwonko ni uburyo bw'ibisubizo by'indwara y'umwijima aho haboneka ubwoko bwose bwa cytokines zirimo TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ na MCP-1.
Iyi mitokine ituma ingirabuzimafatizo z'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri zisohora umubare munini w'imikorere y'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, ari na yo mpamvu nyamukuru ituma habaho ARDS n'ubumuga bw'ingingo nyinshi.
Immunosuppression ni ingenzi mu kuvura indwara ya cytokine, cyane cyane ku ndwara zikomeye.
Kortikosteroide na tocilizumab, agakingirizo ka monoclonal karwanya IL6, zakoreshejwe mu kuvura ihungabana ry'imikorere y'ingirabuzima fatizo.
Ubundi buryo bwo kurwanya ubwirinzi bw'umubiri mu gihe cy'ihungabana ry'ingirabuzimafatizo harimo uburyo bwo guhinduranya ubwirinzi bw'umubiri bukoreshejwe ingirabuzimafatizo za T, gukumira ingirabuzimafatizo za IFN-γ, IL-1 na TNF, gukumira ingirabuzimafatizo za JAK, blinatumomab, ikandamiza ry'ibimenyetso bya sitokini 4 n'ibibuza dHDAC.
Imiti ya steroide, nk'imiti igabanya ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri, yakoreshejwe cyane mu kuvura SARS mu rwego rwo kugabanya ubukana bw'indwara ziterwa n'ubushyuhe.
Ariko, gukoresha imiti ya steroid mu rugero rwagutse nta nyungu byatanze ku gikomere gikomeye cy'ibihaha mu barwayi ba SARS na COVID-19.
Ahubwo, byatera ingaruka mbi cyane zirimo osteonecrosis avascular, bityo bikagira ingaruka zikomeye ku isuzuma ry'ubuzima.
Nyamara, hakomeje gutangwa inama yo gukoresha neza imiti ya corticosteroid mu buryo buringaniye cyangwa buciriritse ku barwayi bafite COVID-19 ikomeye.
Mu gihe iyi raporo yandikwaga, nta muti uvura virusi wari waremejwe ko ugira ingaruka nziza.
Ariko, gutanga remdesivir mu mishipa, ikoreshwa nk'iyo muri nucleoside, byagize ingaruka nziza ku murwayi wo muri Amerika wa COVID-19.
Remdesivir ni umuti mushya uvura virusi watangijwe na Gilead mu kuvura indwara ziterwa na virusi ya Ebola na Marburg.
Nyuma y'aho, remdesivir yagaragaje ko ishobora no guhagarika izindi virusi za RNA z'imiterere imwe, harimo MERS na SARS.
Nyuma y'ibyo byavumbuwe, Gilead yahaye Ubushinwa uyu muti kugira ngo ukorerwe ibizamini ku bantu banduye SARS-CoV-2, kandi ibizamini byitezwe cyane.
Ku rundi ruhande, baricitinib, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir no ribavirine byatanzwe nk' uburyo bushobora gukoreshwa mu kuvura abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero bukabije.
Diyabete, kugira iseseme, kuruka, kwangirika kw'umwijima n'izindi ngaruka mbi bishobora kubaho nyuma yo gufata imiti ihuriweho na lopinavir/ritonavir.
Uburyo uyu muti utera n'indi miti ikoreshwa n'abarwayi bigomba gukurikiranwa neza.
Plasma y'abarwayi bakize n'umusemburo w'abasirikare b'umubiri
Gukuramo amaraso y'abarwayi bakize indwara yandura kugira ngo bavurwe n'abandi barwaye indwara nk'iyo cyangwa ngo barinde abandi bantu bafite ubuzima bwiza indwara yandura, ni umugenzo w'igihe kirekire.
Ni uko abarwayi bakira akenshi baba bafite umubare munini w'abasirikare barwanya virusi itera indwara.
Imirambo ni immunoglobuline (Ig) ikorwa na lymphocytes B kugira ngo irwanye udukoko dutera indwara n'ibindi byanduza umubiri; izi mbaraga zisanzwe muri utwo dukoko kandi zifata utwo dukoko twonyine.
Ibipimo by'amaraso byakuwe mu maraso y'itsinda ry'abarwayi bakize COVID-19 maze bishyirwa mu barwayi 10 bari barembye.
Ibimenyetso byabo byagiye bihinduka nyuma y'amasaha 24 gusa, bigahurirana no kugabanuka kw'ubushyuhe, kugabanuka kw'umubare w'abandura virusi n'izamuka ry'umwuka wa ogisijeni mu maraso.
Ariko, hakenewe igenzura n'ibisobanuro kugirango uburyo bwo gukoreshwa ku rwego runini bushobore gutangwa mu gihe nta muti wihariye umaze gukorwa.
Byongeye kandi, bitewe n'imikorere y'ubuvuzi, hari ingaruka mbi zishobora guterwa na plasma zigomba kwitabwaho.
Urugero, abasirikare b'umubiri bashobora gutuma abasirikare b'umubiri bagira imbaraga nyinshi cyane, bigatuma habaho indwara y'amaraso ishobora guhitana umuntu.
Ubusanzwe amaraso aba afite abasirikare b'umubiri bake, kandi hakenewe cyane plasma mu kuvura abarwayi barwaye cyane.
Biragoye gukora no gukora abashobora kurwanya indwara mu buryo bwihariye vuba bihagije kugira ngo barwanye icyorezo cyugarije isi.
Ni yo mpamvu ari ngombwa kandi ari ingirakamaro cyane gutandukanya B-cells z'abarwayi bakize no kumenya kode z'imiterere z'umubiri z'abasirikare ba virusi cyangwa gushaka abasirikare b'umubiri ba virusi bashobora kurwanya poroteyine z'ingenzi za virusi.
Ibi byatuma habaho kongera vuba umusaruro w'abasirikare b'umubiri.
Mu Bushinwa, TCM imaze imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi ikoreshwa mu kuvura indwara zitandukanye.
Ariko kandi, ingaruka zayo ahanini zishingiye ku guhuza ibintu byinshi mu buryo butandukanye bitewe n'uburwayi bw'umurwayi, bushingiye ku bitekerezo bya TCM.
Ibyinshi mu bice by'ingenzi bikora bikomeza kumenyekana bike cyangwa nta n'ubwo bizwi, kubera ko bigoye kubikuramo no kubigenzura, cyangwa kumenya imiterere yabyo.
Muri iki gihe, kubera ko nta muti wihariye wa COVID-19 urimo gukorwa, MTC ni bumwe mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi bwihuse bukoreshwa ku barwayi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa by'indwara ikomeye.
Urugero, udupfukamunwa twa Shu Feng Jie Du na Lian Hua Qing Wen twafashije cyane mu kuvura COVID-19.
Imirenge yo mu Bushinwa ifite igipimo cyo gukira COVID-19 cyiza cyane ni iya Gansu (63,7%), Ningxia (50%) na Hunan (50%) aho abagera kuri 87% bakoresheje TCM, mu gihe intara ya Hubei yakoresheje 30% gusa by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 ari yo ifite igipimo cyo gukira gito cyane (13%).
Ariko kandi, iyi ni imibare igaragaza uko ibintu bimeze, kuko hari ibindi bintu byinshi bigira ingaruka, urugero nk'umubare w'abarwayi n'ubukana bw'indwara, bigomba kwitabwaho mu gihe umuntu agenzurwa.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Boli Zhang n'abakozi be batangaje ubushakashatsi bugereranya uburyo bwo kuvura bukoresha imiti y'iburengerazuba (MO) gusa n'uburyo bwo kuvura buvanze MO na TCM.
Byagaragaye ko igihe cyo kugaruka ku gipimo gisanzwe cy'ubushyuhe bw'umubiri, igihe cyo kuva ku bimenyetso n'igihe cyo kujya mu bitaro ari kigufi cyane mu itsinda rya MO+MTC kurusha mu itsinda rya MO gusa.
Igitangaje kurushaho, ni uko ikigero cy'indwara z'indwara z'indwara (zivuye ku zoroheje kugera ku z'indwara zikomeye) cyari hasi cyane mu itsinda rya MO+MTC, ugereranyije n'iry'abari mu itsinda MO gusa (7,4% ugereranyije na 46,2%); kandi igipimo cy'abapfuye cyari hasi mu itsinda MO+MTC ugereranyije n'iry'abari mu itsinda MO gusa (8,8% ugereranyije na 39%).
Icyakora, ubuziranenge n'umutekano bya TCM bikiri mu bigomba kugenzurwa mu bigeragezo by'ubugenzuzi ku rwego runini kandi mu bigo byinshi.
Byaba kandi byiza kumenya imikorere y'ibikorwa no gusobanura neza ibice by'ubuvuzi bifatika byo mu miti ya TCM cyangwa imikoranire yayo, niba bishoboka.
