Ni yo mpamvu, ubutabazi bwo mu mutwe bugomba guhabwa abarwayi ba COVID-19, abantu bagaragaye ko bashobora kuba baranduye, abantu bahuye n'abo bantu, n'abandi bantu bafite ibibazo.
Ubufasha bw'imyitwarire bugomba kuba burimo guhugura amakipe y'abantu benshi, itumanaho ridaca ku ruhande riherekejwe n'amakuru mashya kandi y'ukuri ajyanye n'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 n'uburyo bwo kuyivura, ndetse no gukoresha porogaramu n'ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga kugira ngo birinde gukorana n'abantu benshi.
Inkingo zikora neza ni ingenzi mu guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'indwara mu nyamaswa no mu bantu zigera ku bantu bafite ibyago, kandi akenshi zikoreshwa mu kurwanya ibyorezo biterwa na virusi nshya.
Hakozwe ibishoboka byose kugira ngo hashakwe inkingo z'inkingo z'umwimerere S, hagamijwe gukora udukingirizo dufite ubushobozi bwo kurinda virusi igihe kirekire kandi/cyangwa gukingira SARS-CoV.
Inkingo nzima zidakoreshejwe mu buryo bukomeye zagenzuwe mu nyamaswa mu rwego rwo kurwanya SARS.
Ariko, ubuziranenge bwa in vivo bw'izi nkingo zishobora gukoreshwa mu bantu bageze mu za bukuru no mu mikorobe z'abantu zifite ingaruka mbi, ndetse n'ubudahangarwa ku bwandu bw'agakoko gatera indwara y'abantu, biracyari ngombwa ko bigaragazwa, kuko nta bushakashatsi mu rwego rwo gupima abantu bwabaye.
Ibi bishobora kuba biterwa n'uko SARS imaze imyaka 17 yarazimye kandi kuva icyo gihe nta kindi cyorezo cyigeze kivugwa.
Ariko, abantu bakomeje kwandura MERS ku buryo budahindagurika no kuyandura mu Burasirazuba bwo hagati no mu tundi turere bitewe n'uko inzoka zikiriho mu turere twiganjemo indwara.
Hakozwe ingamba zitandukanye zo gukingira MERS hifashishijwe virusi ya inactivated, ADN ya plasmide, ibikoresho bitwara virusi, uduhimba duto cyane, uduhimba twa virusi na poroteyine z'ingingo ntoya, kandi zimwe muri zo zagejejwe ku nyamaswa.
Gushyiraho urukingo rw'ikizere kandi rukora neza rwa SARS-CoV-2 ku bantu batarakingirwa ni intego yihutirwa kandi y'ingenzi mu rwego rwo kurwanya icyorezo kiriho.
Icyakora, iki ni ikibazo gikomeye bitewe n'igihe kirekire cyo gukora urukingo (ugereranyije amezi 18) n'uburyo coronavirus yihindura.
Kubera ko iyi ndwara ari nshya, COVID-19 itangira gusa mu gihe cyo kugerageza kwa muganga ku bantu babarirwa mu bihumbi.
Akenshi, abarwayi bagenda bagaruka ku murongo buhoro buhoro nta ngaruka mbi.
Ariko, kimwe na SARS na MERS, COVID-19 nayo ifitanye isano n'ubwandu n'iyicwa ry'abantu benshi cyane barwaye.
Ni yo mpamvu, gushyiraho uburyo bwo kubara igihe kizaza ari ingenzi kugira ngo ibigo by'ubuzima bishobore gushyira imbere serivisi zabo, cyane cyane mu duce dufite amikoro make.
