Abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane bari bafite ibyago byinshi byo kugira izindi ndwara n'uburwayi bukomeye, kandi bari bakuru cyane (imyaka yo hagati ni 66 n'imyaka 51), ibyo bikaba byerekana ko imyaka ari yo ishobora gutuma abarwayi ba COVID-19 barwara.
