Ni ngombwa kumenya ko imyaka n'uburwayi by'indwara z'ibanze bifitanye isano kandi bishobora guhangana.
Ibisubizo bya laboratwari bidasanzwe: igipimo cya poroteyine yitwa C-reactive (CRP) mu maraso kigaragaza uburemere bw'ubushye cyangwa ubukana bw'uruhu; cyagaragajwe nk'igisubizo gishobora kwemeza indwara, uburyo umuntu azakira n'uburyo azakira.
Hari n'ibyatangajwe ko hari isano iri hagati y'umubare wa CRP n'uburemere ndetse n'uko COVID-19 ishobora kumera.
Ikindi kandi, ubuke bw'ubwoko bwa lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), alanine aminotransferase (ALT) na creatine kinase (CK) na bwo bushobora kugira uruhare mu kugaragaza ibyago.
Izi enzymes zigaragara cyane mu ngingo zitandukanye, cyane cyane mu mutima no mu gihaha, kandi zikarekurwa mu gihe imitsi yangiritse.
Ni yo mpamvu ari ibimenyetso by'indwara y'umutima cyangwa se y'umwijima.
Ibimenyetso by'ingenzi: ibisubizo bya radiographie y'umurava n'uko ibimenyetso by'indwara bigenda bigomba gusuzumwa hamwe n'ibindi byose mu gusuzuma imiterere y'indwara ya COVID-19 n'ingaruka zayo.
Gukoresha Steroide: Nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, steroide ni imiti igabanya ubwirinzi bw'umubiri ikoreshwa cyane nk'imiti y'inyongera mu kuvura indwara z'ibyorezo kugira ngo igabanye uburemere bw'indwara ziterwa n'ubwandu.
Kubera ko imiti ya kortikosteroide ifite ingero nyinshi yakoreshejwe mu kuvura abantu bafite SARS ikomeye, abenshi mu barokotse bagaragaje uburwayi bw'amagufa y'imitsi y'amaraso (osteonecrosis avasculaire) butuma bagira ubumuga bw'iteka kandi bakabaho nabi.
Ni yo mpamvu, iyo bibaye ngombwa, abarwayi ba COVID-19 bagomba guhabwa imiti yo mu bwoko bwa steroid mu rugero ruto kandi mu gihe gito.
Umunaniro wo mu mutwe: nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateje ibibazo byinshi by'ihungabana, abarwayi bakunze kumara igihe kirekire bari mu kato, ntibamenye neza uko bizagenda, ndetse n'ababo cyangwa abandi barwayi bapfuye.
