Ni yo mpamvu abantu baheruka kwandura cyangwa bari mu gihe cyo kwandura bashobora kwanduza virusi nyinshi mu bikorwa byabo bya buri munsi, ibyo bigatuma kurwanya icyorezo bigorana cyane.
Nyamara, SARS-CoV yari igaragaye ko yandura mu barwayi barwaye cyane, kandi bishoboka ko yandura mu cyiciro cya mbere ari nke cyane.
Ni yo mpamvu icyorezo cya COVID-19 cy'ubu ari kibi cyane kandi bigoye kugenzura kurusha icya SARS.
