Uburyo bwa mbere bushoboka bwo kwirinda kugira ngo umuntu agabanye ibyago byo kwandura ni ukwambara udupfukamunwa; gukoresha udupfukamunwa two mu buryo bwo kubaga n'udupfukamunwa two guhumeka twa N95 (1860) birafasha mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
