Kubera ko iyi virusi isa cyane na SARS-CoV kandi ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bikaba ari na byo bisa n'ibya SARS, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatangiye ku mugaragaro nk'icy'ubundi bushya.
