Iduka rya Costco i Canberra na ryo ryagabanyije umubare w'ibicuruzwa byemerewe gutwara mu masanduku abiri mu cyumweru gishize.
Mu rwego rwo gukomeza kugabanya ibura, Coles yategetse abacuruzi ibicuruzwa binini kurushaho no kongera inshuro byoherezwaho, Woolworths yategetse ko haboneka ibindi bicuruzwa, naho ALDI yashyize ibicuruzwa ku isoko mbere y'igihe mu gikorwa cyo kwamamaza cyari giteganyijwe ku wa Gatatu.
Russell Zimmerman, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishyirahamwe ry'abacuruzi muri Ositaraliya, yavuze ko abacuruzi bagerageza kongera ububiko, ariko ko amategeko y'inama y'akarere agena igihe cyo gutumiza ibicuruzwa mu modoka bituma bigorana.
Yiteze ko ibiciro by'ibikoresho bizamuka, mu gihe abikorera bazaba bagerageza guhaza ibyifuzo, kandi ko hazabaho kugabanuka kw'amafaranga yo kuzamura ibicuruzwa.
Ku wa Kabiri, ALDI yatangaje ko nyuma y'uko amaduka ya mbere yagabanyijwe, amaduka amwe n'amwe adashobora gukora ku wa Gatatu.
Mu nkuru y'ikinyamakuru News.com.au, Dr. Gary Mortimer, inzobere mu bijyanye n'ubucuruzi muri kaminuza ya Queensland ya tekiniki, yavuze ko amaduka ashyiramo ibicuruzwa buri joro.
Yavuze ko impapuro z'isuku ari ibintu binini, bigatuma habaho ibicuruzwa bike cyane, iyo bimaze gutakara, bigasiga imyanya minini ku mashyiga, bigatuma haboneka ubukene.
 Coles na Woolworths batekereza [ko] niba amaduka yuzuye, niba ibicuruzwa nk'impapuro z'isuku n'imiti yica udukoko bishobora [gugucuruzwa] kandi bigatangwa mu bwinshi, bishobora kugabanya ubwoba , Russell Zimmerman yabwiye ABC News.
Uruganda rukora impapuro z'isuku zikoreshwa zongeye gukoreshwa Who Gives a Crap rwatangaje kuwa gatatu ushize ko zitari zigisigaye.
Kimberly-Clark, ikora impapuro z'isuku za Kleenex, na Solaris Paper ikora impapuro z'isuku za Sorbent, byashimangiye ko bakora amasaha 24 kuri 24 kugira ngo bakomeze kubona ibyo bakeneye, nk'uko inkuru dukesha News.com.au ibivuga.
Domain.com, urubuga rw'imisha, rwatangaje ko hari abagurisha imitungo y'amazu batangaga impapuro z'isuku ku buntu ku muntu wa mbere wagize icyo agura mu masoko ya cyamunara muri Melbourne, mu gihe amasoko y'amazu yagurishijwe ari make bitewe n'uko abaguzi bari mu kiruhuko cya nyuma y'icyumweru kirekire cy'umunsi w'abakozi.
Umunara wo ku wa kane w'ikinyamakuru NT News, cyandikirwa i Darwin, cyariho impapuro umunani zari zigenewe gukatwa no gukoreshwa nk'impapuro z'isuku.
Ubucuruzi bwabanje kwanga gushyiraho ingamba, nk'uko byavuzwe na ABC Australia yo ku ya 3 Werurwe, aho batangaje ko batateganyaga gushyiraho ingamba zo kugura.
