Mu buryo nk'ubwo, hanze ya Ositaraliya, ku cyumweru nijoro, byaragaragaye ko isoko ryo mu Bwongereza ryitwa Ocado ryategetse ko impapuro z'isuku za Andres zigomba kuba ari udupaki tubiri tw'impapuro 12.
Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima (WHO) wahise uvuga ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo
Ku wa Gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye Ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryemeje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 (cyatewe na virusi ya SARS-CoV-2) cyugarije isi ari icyorezo.
Nubwo ijambo  icyorezo  ryerekeza gusa ku rugero indwara yandukira, aho kwerekeza ku kuba ibyago by'abantu runaka biri hejuru, OMS yagaragaje ko hakenewe gukangurirwa kw'ubutegetsi:
 Ibihugu byose bishobora guhindura icyerekezo cy'icyorezo.
Umukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, yavuze ko ibihugu bigomba gupima, gupima, kuvura, gushyira mu kato, no guhagurukira abaturage babyo mu rwego rwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
 Dufite impungenge zikomeye, atari ku bipimo biteye ubwoba gusa by'ubwandu n'ubukana, ahubwo no ku bipimo biteye ubwoba by'uko nta gikozwe. 
Tom Frieden, wahoze ari umuyobozi w'Ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, yavuze ko iki cyorezo ari "ikitarigeze kubaho".
Mu magambo yatangajwe na CNN muri Gashyantare, yavuze ko uretse ibicurane, nta yindi virusi yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yigeze igaragara kuva yagera ku isi kugeza ubu.
Ghebreyesus na we yavuze ko "nta cyorezo cya coronavirus twigeze tubona".
Yakomeje agira ati "Ntabwo twigeze tubona icyorezo gishobora gufatwa icyarimwe".
Iyi ndwara yemejwe nk'icyorezo nyuma y'icyemezo cyafashwe na OMS muri Mutarama cyo gutangaza ko ari icyorezo gihangayikishije isi yose.
Umuyobozi w'Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe indwara zandura na za alérgie, Dr. Anthony Fauci, yavuze ku byerekeye iki cyorezo ati: "Mu magambo make, ibintu biragenda birushaho kuba bibi".
Ku wa kane, ikinyamakuru Associated Press cyatangaje ko nibura ku isi hari abantu 126,000 banduye COVID-19, bikaba byarahitanye abantu barenga 4600.
Icyorezo cya koronavirusi 2019-20 ni icyorezo cy'indwara ya koronavirusi cyatangiye kuva mu 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe n'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero iterwa na koronavirusi 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiye kugaragara mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu Bushinwa, mu Ukuboza 2019, cyatangajwe ko ari icyorezo gihangayikishije isi yose ku ya 30 Mutarama 2020, cyemezwa ko ari icyorezo ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri 1.61 miliyoni bagaragaweho n'indwara ya COVID-19 mu bihugu n'uturere 210, abagera ku 97.000 bakaba barapfuye.
Abarwayi bagera ku 364.000 bamaze gukira.
Igiciro cy'abapfa kigereranywa ko kiri kuri 4% mu Bushinwa, mu gihe mu bindi bice by'isi gitandukanye kuva kuri 13.04% muri Alijeriya kugeza kuri 0.08% muri Nouvelle-Zélande.
Ibimenyetso bisanzwe birimo umuriro, inkorora no guhumeka nabi.
Ibyago bishobora guterwa n'indwara y'ibihaha n'indwara y'ubuhumekero.
Igihe kiri hagati yo kwanduzwa no kugaragaza ibimenyetso ni iminsi itanu, ariko gishobora kuva ku minsi ibiri kugeza kuri cumi n'ine.
Nta rukingo cyangwa umuti wihariye uvura iyi virusi uraboneka.
Uburyo bw'ibanze bwo kuvura ni ugukomeza no kuvura mu buryo bw'ibimenyetso. Uburyo bwo kwirinda bwashyizweho burimo gukaraba intoki, gukingisha umunwa igihe ukorora, kwirinda kwegera abandi, no kugenzura no gushyira mu kato abantu bakekwaho kuba baranduye.
Abayobozi ku isi yose babyifashishije bashyiraho ingamba zo guhagarika ingendo, gushyira abantu mu kato, amasaha yo gutaha, kugenzura ibyago byo mu kazi no gufunga ibigo.
Icyorezo cyateje ibibazo bikomeye mu bukungu ku isi, gusubika cyangwa guhagarika ibikorwa bitandukanye birimo siporo, amadini, politiki n'umuco, ndetse n'ubukene bw'ibiribwa bwagaragaye, bukaba bwarushijeho kwiyongera bitewe n'abantu bagurishaga ibintu mu buryo butari bwo.
Amashuri na kaminuza byafunze mu bihugu 193 cyangwa mu turere twaho, bigira ingaruka ku kigero cya 99,4% by'abanyeshuri ku isi.
Amakuru atari yo ku byerekeye iyi virusi yakwirakwijwe kuri interineti, kandi habayeho ibikorwa byo kwanga no gukumira by'urwikekwe Abashinwa, abandi bantu bakomoka cyangwa bagaragara ko bakomoka mu Burasirazuba no mu Majyepfo y'Iburasirazuba bwa Aziya, n'abandi bantu baturutse mu turere dufite umubare munini w'abantu banduye.
Kubera ko ingendo zagabanutse n'inganda zikomeye zifunga, habonetse igabanuka ry'umwuka uhumanye hamwe n'imyuka ya karuboni.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, inzego z'ubuzima zo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu Bushinwa (umurwa mukuru w'intara ya Hubei) zatangaje ko hari umuntu wanduye umusonga ufite impamvu itaramenyekana, maze mu ntangiriro za Mutarama 2020 hatangira iperereza.
Benshi muri abo barwayi ni abacuruzaga amafi yo mu nyanja mu mujyi wa Huanan, bityo bikaba byemezwa ko virusi ishobora kuba yaraturutse ku nyamaswa.
Virusi yateje iki cyorezo ni SARS-CoV-2, virusi iherutse kuvumburwa kandi ifitanye isano rya hafi na koronavirusi y'igishwi, koronavirusi y'ingona, na SARS-CoV. Nyuma byaje kumenyekana ko umuntu wa mbere uzwi wagaragaje ibimenyetso yafashwe n'iyi ndwara ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019, kandi uwo muntu nta sano rigaragara yari afitanye n'isoko ry'ibikomoka ku biribwa.
Muri izo mpinduka za mbere zavuzwe mu Ukuboza 2019, bibiri bya gatatu byabonetse ko bifitanye isano n'isoko.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, hari raporo itavugurujwe mu kinyamakuru cya South China Morning Post ivuga ko umuntu wa mbere wabonetse mu kwezi kwa 11 2019, ni umugabo w'imyaka 55 wo mu ntara ya Hubei. Ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020, OMS yatangaje ko kubera ko abanduye bashya bari baragabanutse mu Bushinwa ariko mu buryo butunguranye bariyongera mu Butaliyani, Irani na Koreya y'Epfo, umubare w'abanduye bashya hanze y'Ubushinwa warenze ku nshuro ya mbere umubare w'abanduye bashya mu Bushinwa.
Hari aho habaho kugabanya cyane umubare w'abanduye, cyane cyane mu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje.
Ku ya 26 Gashyantare, umubare muto w'abanduye wari umaze kumenyekana mu rubyiruko, abafite imyaka 19 no munsi yayo bagize 2.4% by'abanduye ku isi. Umujyanama mukuru mu bya siyansi mu Bwongereza, Patrick Vallance, yavuze ko 60% by'abatuye Ubwongereza bagomba kuba banduye mbere y'uko ubwirinzi bw'imbaga bugera ku rugero rwiza.
Abanduye ni umubare w'abantu bapimwe COVID-19, maze bagasanga bafite COVID-19 hakurikijwe amabwiriza yemewe.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyasuzumye abaturage bacyo barenze 3%, kandi ibihugu byinshi byari bifite politiki yo kudahita abantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje, urugero nk'Ubutaliyani, u Buholandi, Esipanye n'u Busuwisi.
Ubushakashatsi bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku ya 16 Werurwe, bwagaragaje ko mu Bushinwa, kugeza ku ya 23 Mutarama, abantu bagera kuri 86% by'abanduye COVID-19 batamenyekanye, kandi ko 79% by'abanduye banditswe, babiterwa n'ubwandu butari bwagaragazwa.
Isesengura ry'imibare ryasohotse ku ya 30 Werurwe ryagaragaje ko umubare w'ubwandu mu Butaliyani ari munini cyane ugereranyije n'abari baburiwe.
Ibipimo by'ibanze by'ubwiyongere (R0) bwa COVID-19 byari hagati ya 1,4 na 2,4.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara bwavuze ko bishobora kuba 5.7.
Abantu benshi barwaye COVID-19 barakira.
Ku bantu batakira, igihe hagati y'intangiriro y'ibimenyetso n'urupfu kiri hagati y'iminsi 6 na 41, ubusanzwe ni iminsi 14.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera ku 97.000 bari bamaze guhitanwa na COVID-19.
Mu Bushinwa, ku ya 5 Gashyantare, hafi 80% by'abapfuye bari abantu bari hejuru y'imyaka 60, naho 75% bari bafite ibibazo by'ubuzima nk'indwara z'umutima na diyabete. Umubare w'abapfuye bishwe n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 ubusanzwe werekeza ku bapfuye basuzumwe bagasanga baranduye COVID-19 hakurikijwe amabwiriza yemewe.
Umubare nyawo w'abishwe na COVID-19 ushobora kuba uruta uwo kuko ushobora kuba utabarura abantu bapfuye batapimwe - urugero, bapfiriye mu ngo zabo, mu bigo byita ku bageze mu za bukuru n'ahandi.
Ibipimo by'ibanze byo mu Butaliyani byerekana ko umubare w'abapfuye muri iki cyorezo wikubye inshuro 4 cyangwa 5 uw'abapfuye bishwe na COVID.
Umuvugizi w'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) yemeye  Tuzi ko [umubare w'abapfuye watangajwe] ari muke , ibyo bikaba byemezwa n'amakuru y'ibyabaye muri Amerika. Gukabya gukabya akenshi bibaho mu gihe cy'icyorezo, nk'icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube cya H1N1 cyo mu 2009.
Umuntu wa mbere wapfuye hanze y'Ubushinwa yapfuye tariki ya 1 Gashyantare muri Filipine, naho uwa mbere wapfuye hanze ya Aziya apfa ku ya 14 Gashyantare mu Bufaransa.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, hanze y'u Bushinwa, abantu barenga cumi na babiri muri buri gihugu bari bamaze guhitanwa n'icyorezo muri Irani, Koreya y'Epfo n'u Butaliyani.
Kugeza ku ya 13 Werurwe, ibihugu n'intara bisaga mirongo ine byari byaravuze ko abantu bapfuye, ku migabane yose uretse Antaragitika. Hari ibimenyetso byinshi bikoreshwa mu kugenzura umubare w'abapfuye.
Iyi mibare iratandukana bitewe n'akarere n'igihe, kandi igaterwa n'umubare w'abemezwa ko bapimwe, ubuvuzi bwiza, uburyo bwo kuvura, igihe icyorezo cyamaze, n'ibintu biranga abantu, urugero nk'imyaka, igitsina, n'ubuzima. Umubare w'abapfuye ugereranya umubare w'abapfuye ugabanijwe n'umubare w'abanduye mu gihe runaka.
Nk'uko bigaragara mu mibare ya kaminuza ya Johns-Hopkins, umubare w'abanduye ku isi wari ku kigero cya 6.0% (97 039/1 617 204) ku ya 10 Mata 2020.
Umubare w'abapfuye uratandukana bitewe n'akarere.
Mu Bushinwa, imibare y'umubare w'abanduye n'abapfuye yagabanutseho 17,3% (ku bantu bagaragaje ibimenyetso hagati ya 1-10 Mutarama 2020) igera kuri 0,7% (ku bantu bagaragaje ibimenyetso nyuma ya 1 Gashyantare 2020). Izindi ngero ni urugero rw'abahitanwa n'indwara (urugero rw'abahitanwa n'indwara), rugaragaza umubare w'abamenye ko bafite indwara ariko bagapfa, n'urugero rw'abandura (urugero rw'abanduye) rugaragaza umubare w'abanduye (ba barwaye cyangwa bataravurwa) bapfa.
Iyi mibare ntabwo ifitanye isano n'igihe kandi igaragaza umubare w'abantu runaka banduye nyuma y'indwara.
Abahanga mu bya siyansi benshi bagerageje kubara imibare y'ibyo bintu ku bantu runaka.
Ikigo gishinzwe ubuvuzi bushingiye ku bimenyetso cya kaminuza ya Oxford gitekereza ko ubwandu muri rusange buri hagati ya 0.1% na 0.39%.
Igiciro cyo hejuru muri ibyo biciro gihuza n'ibyavuye mu bipimo bya mbere byafashwe ku bushake bya COVID-19 mu Budage, n'ubushakashatsi bw'ibarurishamibare busuzuma ingaruka z'ibizamini ku gipimo cy'abapfa.
OMS ivuga ko icyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa.
Ikigero cy'icyorezo n'igihe kizarangira ntibiramenyekana neza kandi gishobora gutandukana bitewe n'akarere.
Maciej Boni wo muri Pennsylvania State University yagize ati:  Iyo indwara zidakurikizwa, ubusanzwe indwara zandura zirakomera, hanyuma zigatangira kugabanuka iyo indwara igeze aho itagishobora kuba yakira.
Ariko biragoye cyane ko umuntu yakwibaza igihe ibi bizaba bizasohorera.
Umujyanama mukuru mu by'ubuvuzi wa leta y'Ubushinwa Zhong Nanshan yavuze ko "bishobora kurangira mu kwezi kwa Kamena" mu gihe ibihugu byose byafata ingamba zikwiye zo gukurikiza amabwiriza ya OMS ku ngamba zo gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi".
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, Adam Kucharski wo mu Ishuri ry'Ubuziranenge n'Ubuvuzi bwo mu Bihe Bishyuhe ry'i Londres yavuze ko SARS-CoV-2  izakomeza gukwirakwira, wenda mu gihe cy'umwaka umwe cyangwa ibiri .
Nk'uko bigaragazwa n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Neil Ferguson wo muri kaminuza ya Imperial, kwirinda kwegerana n'abandi no gufata ingamba z'isuku bizakenerwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba ruhari (bishobora kuba mu mezi 18 cyangwa arenga).
William Schaffner wo muri Kaminuza ya Vanderbilt yagize ati: "Ndatekereza ko iyi virusi ya corona idashobora kuba yarakwirakwizwa cyane" "kugira ngo izapfe burundu" kandi ko "ishobora kuba indwara y'igihe cy'umwaka, ishobora kugaruka buri mwaka".
Uko ubu busubiranamo buzabaho bizaterwa n'ubushobozi bw'ubwandu n'ubw'ubwandu bw'ubwandu.
Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 rimwe na rimwe ntibiragaragara neza kandi abantu banduye bashobora kuba nta bimenyetso bagaragaza.
Ibimenyetso bibiri by'indwara bikunze kugaragara ni umuriro (88%) n'inkorora idakama (68%).
Ibimenyetso bikunze kugaragara harimo umunaniro, gusohora kw'imyanya y'ubuhumekero (mucus), gutakaza impumuro, guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu ngingo no mu ngingo, kubabara mu muhogo, kurwara umutwe, guhinda umushyitsi, gusesa, kuva amaraso menshi, kuribwa cyangwa guhinda umushyitsi. OMS ivuga ko hafi umuntu umwe kuri batandatu aba arwaye cyane kandi afite ibibazo byo guhumeka.
Ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no kwirinda indwara (CDC) kigaragaza ibimenyetso byihutirwa birimo guhumeka nabi, ububabare cyangwa umuvuduko w'igituza ukomeza, urujijo rutunguranye, gukanguka mu gihe cy'ububyutse, n'uruhu cyangwa iminwa bihinduka ubururu; iyo ibyo bimenyetso bibonetse, ni byiza ko byihutirwa kwitabwaho n'abaganga. Uko indwara ikomeza gutera bishobora gutuma umuntu aba afite umusonga ukabije, indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero, indwara y'umuhogo, guhumanywa n'imyanda no gupfa.
Bamwe mu banduye bashobora kuba nta bimenyetso, nta bimenyetso by'indwara, ariko bagatanga ibisubizo by'ibizamini byemeza ko banduye, bityo abashakashatsi batanze inama ko abantu bahuye bya hafi n'abantu bemejwe ko banduye bagomba gukurikiranwa hafi no gusuzumwa kugira ngo barebe niba hari ibyago byo kwandura.
Ubushinwa buvuga ko umubare w'abatabyerekanyeho ibimenyetso uri hagati ya bake na 44%.
Igihe gisanzwe cyo kubura impumuro (igihe hagati yo kwandura no kugaragaza ibimenyetso) kiri hagati y'umunsi umwe na 14; akenshi ni iminsi itanu. Urugero rw'ibitaragenze neza, umubare w'abantu bafite COVID-19 batakaje ubushobozi bwo guhumurirwa wari wavuye kuri 30% ugashyirwa kuri 15%.
Kugeza ubu, hari amakuru menshi ataramenyekana ku bijyanye n'uburyo iyi ndwara ikwirakwira.
Bivugwa ko ubwandu bw'iyi ndwara buturuka ahanini ku guhura hafi no ku matembabuzi mato cyane cyane umuntu akayafite, akihumura cyangwa avuze; aho umuntu ahurira hafi cyane ni muri metero 1 cyangwa 2 (3 kugeza kuri 6 ft).
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko umuntu ukorora atabyitondeye ashobora kujugunya utwo tugufi ku burebure bwa metero 4,5 kugeza kuri metero 8.2.
Hari abatekereza ko virusi ishobora kwandura kandi binyuze mu matembabuzi y'amazi amara igihe kirekire mu kirere, ashobora gusohoka mu gihe umuntu avuze. Matembabuzi y'umwuka ashobora gusohoka mu muhogo, cyane cyane mu gihe umuntu avuze, nubwo virusi idakunze gutwarwa n'indege.
Ibicanwa bishobora kugwa mu kanwa cyangwa mu mazuru y'abandi bantu bari iruhande cyangwa se bikajya mu bihaha.
Bimwe mu bikorwa byo kwa muganga nko gutera intoki mu mubiri no guhumeka (CPR) bishobora gutuma udukoko two mu myanya y'ubuhumekero duturika, bityo tukandura mu mwuka.
Ishobora kandi gukwirakwira igihe umuntu akoze ku kintu cyanduye, cyane cyane ku ruhu, mbere yo gukora ku maso, ku mazuru cyangwa ku munwa.
Nubwo hari impungenge ko ishobora kwanduzwa n'ibishishi, iyi ndwara ifatwa nk'aho ari nke.
Guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yanze ko SARS-CoV-2 yandura mu kanwa binyuze mu myanya y'ubuhumekero. Virusi yandura cyane mu minsi itatu ya mbere ibimenyetso byatangiye kugaragara, ariko ikwirakwira rishobora kubaho mbere y'uko ibimenyetso by'indwara biboneka no mu bihe bya nyuma by'indwara.
Abantu bagaragayeho ubwandu mu minsi itatu mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira, bikaba byerekana ko ubwandu bushobora kubaho mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bifatika bitangira.
Hari raporo nke z'abantu bafite ibimenyetso byemejwe muri laboratwari, ariko kwanduzanya kutagaragaza ibimenyetso byabonetse mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe mu gihe cy'iperereza ryo gushakisha abahuye n'abantu.
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC) kivuga ko nubwo bitaramenyekana neza uburyo iyi ndwara yandurira mu buryo bworoshye, ubusanzwe umuntu umwe yandurira abandi bantu babiri cyangwa batatu. Virusi ishobora kumara amasaha cyangwa iminsi ku bintu.
Mu buryo bwihariye, virusi yashoboye kuboneka nyuma y'iminsi itatu ku mupira (polypropylene) na 304 ibyuma bitagira ingeso, nyuma y'umunsi umwe ku ikarito, no nyuma y'amasaha ane ku muringa.
Ariko, ibi biterwa n'ubushyuhe n'ubushyuhe. Hari inyamaswa zo mu rugo n'izindi zisuzumweho COVID-19.
