Ibihugu n'uturere bigera kuri 200 byagize nibura umuntu umwe wanduye.
Kubera icyorezo cyugarije u Burayi, ibihugu byinshi biri mu karere ka Schengen byafunze ingendo kandi bishyiraho uburyo bwo kugenzura imipaka.
Mu buryo bw'igihugu, harimo ingamba zo kwirinda nk'uko abantu bashyirwa mu kato (zitwa Guma mu Rugo, Gutaha, cyangwa Gufunga) n'amasaha yo gutaha. Ku ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera hafi kuri miliyoni 300, cyangwa hafi 90% by'abaturage, bari mu buryo runaka bwo kwirinda muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 bari mu kato muri Filipine, miliyoni 59 muri Afurika y'Epfo na miliyari 1,3 mu Buhinde.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi bari mu bihe by'akato, umubare wageze kuri miliyari 2.6 nyuma y'iminsi ibiri - hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko arwaye COVID-19 yabayeho ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan; hari raporo itemejwe igaragaza ko umuntu wa mbere wanduye COVID-19 yabayeho ku ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Dr. Zhang Jixian yabonye umuntu ufite ikibazo cy'indwara y'igifu ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, kandi amenyesha CDC y'i Wuhan Jianghan ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ibizamini bya mbere by'imiterere y'ibipimo by'abarwayi ku ya 27 Ukuboza 2019 byagaragaje ko hari coronavirus isa na SARS.
Komisiyo y'ubuzima ya komini ya Wuhan yasohoye itangazo rusange ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza.
WHO yamenyeshejwe kuri uwo munsi.
Abaganga bo muri Wuhan bahawe umuburo kubera gukwirakwiza ibihuha ku cyorezo.
Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa mu mizo ya mbere yavuze ko nta gihamya igaragara y'uko abantu bandura.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'u Bushinwa yatangiye ubukangurambaga bw'imbaraga, nyuma y'aho Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti b'u Bushinwa, Xi Jinping, yabwise "Intambara y'abaturage" yo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Mu cyiswe "karantine nini mu mateka y'abantu", ku ya 23 Mutarama hatangajwe ko abantu bagomba kujya mu kato kugira ngo bahagarike ingendo ziva no kugera i Wuhan, kandi byatangiye kugera ku mijyi 15 no muri Hubei, bigera ku bantu bagera kuri miriyoni 57.
Gukoresha imodoka bwite byarabujijwe mu mujyi.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa (kuwa 25 Mutarama) byakuweho mu duce twinshi.
Abayobozi kandi batangaje ko bagiye kubaka ivuriro ry'agateganyo ryitwa Huoshenshan, ryarangiye mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hubatswe iyindi bitaro yitwa Leishenshan kugira ngo haboneke abarwayi benshi.
Usibye ibitaro bishya, Ubushinwa bwahinduye izindi nyubako 14 muri Wuhan, zirimo ibigo by'amakoraniro n'ibibuga by'imikino, ngo bibe ibitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yashyizeho ingamba nshya zo kurwanya icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo no gutanga raporo y'ubuzima ku bantu bakora ingendo no kongera iminsi y'ikiruhuko cy'umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi.
Kaminuza n'amashuri yo muri icyo gihugu na byo byafunzwe.
Akarere ka Hong Kong na Macao zashyizeho ingamba nyinshi, cyane cyane ku mashuri na za kaminuza.
Ibigo by'ubwikorezi bw'amafaranga byatangijwe mu duce dutandukanye two mu Bushinwa.
Ingamba zo gukumira ingendo zashyizweho muri Hubei no hanze yayo.
Ingendo zo gutwara abantu mu buryo bwa rusange zarabujijwe, kandi ingoro ndangamurage zo mu Bushinwa zifunze by'agateganyo.
Mu mijyi myinshi hashyizweho uburyo bwo kugenzura ingendo z'abaturage, kandi byemezwa ko abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (ni ukuvuga abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bagizweho n'uburyo bumwe cyangwa ubundi bw'ibihano byo kutavugana. Nyuma y'uko icyorezo cyateye ku isi muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'u Bushinwa bashyizeho ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda ko virusi yanduzwa mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho gahunda yo gushyira mu kato iminsi 14 ku bantu bose baturuka mu mahanga binjira mu mujyi. Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, mu Bushinwa, hari umuntu umwe gusa wari umaze kwandura mu minsi itanu yari ishize, akaba yari yanduye ku muntu wari uvuye muri Istanbul asubiye i Guangzhou.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'intebe Li Keqiang yatangaje ko ubwandu bw'abantu banduye mu gihugu bwahagaritswe, kandi ko icyorezo cyagenzurwa mu Bushinwa.
Kuri uwo munsi, ingendo zabujijwe muri Hubei zarorohejwe, usibye Wuhan, nyuma y'amezi abiri ingendo zitangiye. Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ku wa 26 Werurwe 2020 ko kwinjira ku bafite viza cyangwa uruhushya rwo gutura muri icyo gihugu bizaba byahagaritswe guhera ku wa 28 Werurwe, ariko ntiyatangaje igihe iryo tegeko rizarangirira.
Abashaka kwinjira mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba viza muri ambasade cyangwa konsira z'Ubushinwa.
Guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yashishikarije ibigo by'ubucuruzi n'inganda kongera gufungura ku itariki ya 30 Werurwe, kandi itanga gahunda yo kuzamura ubukungu ku bigo by'ubucuruzi. Akanama k'ubutegetsi bw'igihugu katangaje ko umunsi wo kuboroga uzatangira ku itariki ya 4 Mata saa kumi n'iminota itatu, bihuye n'umunsi mukuru wa Qingming, nubwo guverinoma nkuru yasabye imiryango kuboroga bakoresheje interineti kugira ngo bakomeze kwirinda no kwirinda ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyongera kwaduka.
Byaremejwe ko COVID-19 yakwirakwiriye muri Koreya y'Epfo ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020 ivuye mu Bushinwa.
Ikigo gishinzwe ubuzima muri iki gihugu cyatangaje ko umubare w'abamaze kwandura wazamutse cyane ku ya 20 Gashyantare, ahanini bitewe n'iteraniro ryabereye i Daegu ry'umuryango mushya w'idini witwa Shincheonji Church of Jesus.
Abari mu idini rya Shincheonji basuye Daegu baturutse i Wuhan bakekwaho kuba ari bo batumye icyorezo cyaduka.
Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bantu 9,336 bari mu rusengero, 1,261 cyangwa hafi 13 ku ijana bagaragaje ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko hari abantu bafite ikibazo gikomeye cyane ku ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abantu barenga 2000 bemejwe ko banduye muri Koreya, hanyuma ku ya 29 Gashyantare haboneka abantu 3150.
Inzego za gisirikare zose muri Koreya y'Epfo zafatiwe mu kato nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu bapimwe bagasanga banduye virusi ya corona.
Ibihe by'indege na byo byagizweho ingaruka, bituma bihinduka. Koreya y'Epfo yatangije icyo abantu batekereza ko ari gahunda yagutse kandi iteganyijwe neza ku isi yo gupima abarwayi, no gushyira mu kato abantu bose banduye no gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abantu bahuye n'abo bantu.
Uburyo bwo gupima burimo gutanga raporo y'ibimenyetso ku muntu ku giti cye ku bantu bashya baje baturutse mu bindi bihugu bifashishije porogaramu ya telefoni, gupima virusi bitanga ibisubizo ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu bagera ku 20.000 buri munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo ifatwa nk'igikorwa cy'ubufatanye mu guhashya icyorezo, nubwo itarimo gushyira mu kato imijyi yose. Mu mizo ya mbere, abaturage ba Koreya y'Epfo bari bafite amacakubiri ku buryo Perezida Moon Jae-in yakiriye iki cyorezo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba ko Moon ashinjwa kuba guverinoma yarakemuye nabi icyorezo cyangwa bashima uko yitwaye.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Koreya y'Epfo yagize umubare muto w'abanduye buri munsi mu byumweru bine bishize.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, hatangajwe ko guhera ku ya 1 Mata, abantu bose bavuye mu mahanga bazajya bashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Amakuru yo mu bitangazamakuru avuga ko ku ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yari imaze kubona ibyifuzo by'ubufasha mu gupima virusi bivuye mu bihugu 121.
Iran yatangaje ko abantu ba mbere banduye SARS-CoV-2 bayanduye ku ya 19 Gashyantare i Qom, aho Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi mu by'Ubuvuzi yavuze ko nyuma y'aho kuri uwo munsi hapfuye abantu babiri.
Ingamba za mbere leta yatangaje harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, siporo n'amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, no gufunga za kaminuza, amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani yashyizeho miriyari eshanu z'amafaranga y'u Rwanda yo kurwanya iyi virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato ibice byibasiwe n'icyorezo, ko abantu bonyine ari bo bazajya bashyirwa mu kato.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, hatangajwe gahunda zo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi, nubwo urujya n'uruza rukomeje kuba rwagutse hagati y'imijyi mu rwego rwo gutegura Umwaka Mushya w'Abaperesi.
Inzu z'abatagatifu z'Abashiya i Qom zakomeje gufungurirwa abasenga kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020. Irani yabaye ihuriro ry'ikwirakwira rya virusi nyuma y'Ubushinwa muri Gashyantare.
Mu gihe habaga hari ibihuha ko hashobora kubaho guhishira ubwandu muri Iran, ku ya 28 Gashyantare, ibihugu birenga icumi byatangaje ko abanduye babonetse muri Iran, byerekana ko icyorezo gishobora kuba gikomeye kurusha abanduye 388 leta ya Iran yari yatangaje kuri iyo tariki.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe nyuma y'uko ku ya 3 Werurwe, abadepite 23 muri 290 bayigize bagaragaje ko banduye virusi.
Ku ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza kurekura byimazeyo abaharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu bafunzwe bazira imyigaragambyo yo mu mahoro, no kurekura by'agateganyo imfungwa zose zujuje ibisabwa.
Umuryango wavuze ko hari ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwira kwa virusi mu bigo bifunze nk'ibigo by'agateganyo, na byo bikaba bidafite ubuvuzi.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye mu munsi umwe, umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye mu gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abanyapolitiki 12 ba kera cyangwa bariho muri iki gihe bo muri Irani n'abayobozi ba leta bapfuye bazize iyi ndwara.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yarimo abantu bashya 50 banduye buri saha, kandi buri minota 10 hapfa umuntu umwe bitewe na koronavirusi.
Nk'uko bivugwa n'umuyobozi wa OMS, muri Irani hashobora kuba hari abanduye inshuro eshanu z'abari bayanduye.
Hasabwe kandi ko ibihano bya Amerika bishobora kubangamira ubushobozi bw'igihugu mu by'imari bwo guhangana n'icyorezo.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku burenganzira bwa muntu ryasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu byoroherezwa ku bihugu byazahajwe cyane n'icyorezo, harimo na Irani.
Byaremejwe ko icyorezo cyakwiriye mu Butaliyani ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubwo ba mukerarugendo babiri b'Abashinwa bapimwaga bagasanga baranduye SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Abanduye batangiye kwiyongera vuba, bituma guverinoma y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose z'indege zijya cyangwa zivuye mu Bushinwa, kandi itangaza ko hari ibyago.
Nyuma y'aho havumbuwe icyorezo cya COVID-19 kitari gifitwe isano, aho tariki ya 21 Gashyantare abantu 16 bo muri Lombardy barwaye. Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rishya rigamije gukumira icyorezo, harimo gushyira mu kato abantu barenga 50 000 bo mu mijyi 11 itandukanye yo mu majyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte yagize ati:  Mu bice byibasiwe n'icyorezo, ntawe uzemererwa kwinjira cyangwa gusohoka.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, guverinoma y'Ubutaliyani yategetse ko amashuri na za kaminuza zose zo mu gihugu bifungwa burundu mu gihe mu Butaliyani hapfuye abantu 100.
Ibirori byose by'imikino, harimo n'imikino y'umupira w'amaguru ya Serie A, byari biteganyijwe ko bizabera mu rugo kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku ya 9 Werurwe, siporo yose yahagaritswe burundu mu gihe cy'ukwezi.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conte yategetse ko ibikorwa byose by'ubucuruzi bihagarikwa, uretse gusa amaduka manini na farumasi. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ishyirahamwe ry'Ubuvuzi bw'Igitsina, Ubuvuzi bw'Ibyuma, Ubuvumbuzi n'Ubuvuzi Bukomeye (SIAARTI) ryasohoye amabwiriza y'imikorere y'ubuvuzi yerekeranye n'uburyo bwo gupima bushobora gukorwa.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, u Butaliyani bwatsinze u Bushinwa mu kugira abantu benshi bapfuye bishwe na koronavirusi ku isi, nyuma yo gutanga raporo y'abantu 3,405 bahitanywe n'icyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, byavuzwe ko Uburusiya bwohereje indege z'ingabo icyenda zari zuzuye ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Kugeza ku ya 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hari abamaze kwandura 128.948, abamaze gupfa ni 15.887 naho abakize ni 21.815, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardy.
Inkuru yatanzwe na CNN yavuze ko kuba mu Butaliyani hari umubare munini w'abantu bageze mu za bukuru, no kuba kugeza ubu abantu bose banduye virusi batarapimwa bishobora kuba ari byo byatumye umubare w'abapfa wiyongera.
Ubwongereza bwabanje kugaragara nk'igihugu cyoroheje cyane mu bihugu byibasiwe n'icyorezo, kandi kugeza ku ya 18 Werurwe 2020, guverinoma y'Ubwongereza ntiyigeze itegeka abaturage bayo kwirinda kwegerana cyangwa gushyira mu kato.
Ku bw'ibyo, guverinoma yanenzwe ko ititabira cyane kandi ko idashishikajwe n'ibibazo by'abaturage. Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatangaje ko abantu bose batagomba gukora ingendo n'indi mirimo itari ngombwa, asaba ko abantu bakorera mu rugo niba bishoboka, kandi bakirinda kujya ahantu hahurira abantu benshi, nko mu tubari, muri resitora no mu mazu y'imikino.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, guverinoma yatangaje ko ibigo byose by'imyidagaduro nka za pub na za siporo byagombaga gufungwa vuba bishoboka, kandi isezeranya ko izatanga 80% by'imishahara y'abakozi, mu gihe kitarenze £2,500 ku kwezi, mu rwego rwo kwirinda ubushomeri bufite aho buhuriye n'ikibazo. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda guhura, abuza guteranira hamwe abantu barenze babiri, no kugabanya ingendo n'ibikorwa byo hanze ku buryo bukenewe.
Mu buryo butandukanye n'ingamba zabanje, ibi bihano byashyizweho n'igipolisi, harimo amande no guseswa kw'iteraniro.
Ibigo byinshi byasabwe gufunga, uretse ibyo byasabwaga gukora by'ingenzi, birimo ibigo by'ubucuruzi, ibigo by'ubucuruzi bw'imiti, amabanki, amaduka acuruza ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga, za sitasiyo za lisansi na gare.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, habonetse umuntu wa mbere wanduye COVID-19 mu majyaruguru y'uburengerazuba bwa Pasifika muri Leta ya Washington, ni umugabo wari wavuye i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Itsinda ry'abakozi bo muri White House rishinzwe kurwanya coronavirus ryashinzwe ku itariki ya 29 Mutarama.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko ari ikibazo cy'ubuzima bw'abaturage kandi bufata ingendo z'abinjira n'abasohoka baturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara, ikigo cy'ingenzi gishinzwe ubuzima muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, cyatangaje ko cyakoze ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi.
Nubwo bimeze bityo ariko, Amerika yatinze gutangira ibizamini, bituma abantu batabona neza uko icyorezo cyari kimeze icyo gihe.
Ibipimo byashyizweho impaka n'ibikoresho byo gupima indwara byakozwe na leta muri Gashyantare, kubura uruhushya rwa leta rwo gupima indwara mu bikoresho byo gupima indwara by'ibigo bitari ibya leta (amashuri, ibigo by'ubucuruzi n'ibitaro) kugeza mu mpera za Gashyantare, n'amabwiriza y'uko umuntu agomba kuba yujuje ibisabwa kugira ngo asuzumwe kugeza mu ntangiriro za Werurwe (gusaba ko umuganga atanga amabwiriza nyuma y'aho).
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, The Washington Post yatangaje ko hari abantu batageze ku 4000 basuzumwe muri Amerika.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru The Atlantic cyatangaje ko hari abantu batageze ku 14,000 bapimwe.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru Associated Press cyatangaje ko: "Abantu benshi bafite ibimenyetso kandi bakaba bari barandikiwe imiti n'abaganga, bategereje amasaha ndetse n'iminsi kugira ngo bapimwe". Nyuma y'urupfu rwa mbere muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika rwatangajwe muri Leta ya Washington ku ya 29 Gashyantare, Guverineri Jay Inslee yatangaje ko igihugu kiri mu bihe bidasanzwe, ibikorwa byahise bikurikirwa n'ibindi bihugu.
Amashuri yo mu gace ka Seattle yasubitse amasomo ku ya 3 Werurwe, maze mu kwezi kwa Werurwe amashuri yo mu gihugu hose arafungwa. Ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020, Amerika yamenyeshejwe iby'ingaruka z'icyorezo cya koronavirusi ku gihugu n'itsinda ry'abahanga mu by'indwara zo mu mutwe bo muri Imperial College London.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko rigena ingengo y'imari y'inyongera yo kurwanya no kurwanya icyorezo cya Koronavirusi, ritanga ingengo y'imari y'ibanze y'amadolari miriyari 8.3 yo gufasha ibigo bya leta guhangana n'icyorezo.
Ibigo byashyizeho amategeko agenga ingendo z'abakozi babyo, byahagaritse inama ndetse byashishikariza abakozi gukorera mu rugo.
Mu gihe ibikorwa by'imikino n'ibihe byahariwe, ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko hari ingendo zahagaritswe mu bihugu byinshi by'u Burayi, uretse u Bwongereza, mu gihe cy'iminsi 30, guhera ku ya 13 Werurwe.
Ku munsi wakurikiyeho, yongereyeho ibihano kugira ngo yongereho Ubwongereza na Irilande.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ko igihugu kiri mu bihe bidasanzwe, bituma haboneka amafaranga y'igihugu yo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Kuva ku ya 15 Werurwe, ibigo byinshi by'ubucuruzi muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika byafunze cyangwa bigabanya amasaha byakoraga kugira ngo bigabanyirize ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyemejwe muri buri leta 50 no mu Karere ka Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, mu mujyi wa New York havugwa abantu 10 700 banduye coronavirus, bakaba baruta umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, guverineri yavuze ko kwirinda kwegerana mu baturage bisa n'ibikora kuko imibare y'ubwiyongere bw'abanduye yavuye ku minsi 2.0 igera ku minsi 4.7.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Werurwe, abantu 32 308 bagaragayeho coronavirus muri New York, abantu 672 bakaba barayimuye. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yari ifite abantu benshi bagaragayeho coronavirus kurusha ibindi bihugu byose ku isi, harimo n'u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Kugeza ku ya 8 Mata, abantu 400 335 bari bayirimo muri Amerika, naho abantu 12 841 bakaba bari bamaze gupfa.
Ku ya 30 Werurwe, binyuze mu itangazamakuru, Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Trump, yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kwirinda kwegerana kugeza ku ya 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi kandi, ubwato bwitwa USNS Comfort, ubwato bw'ibitaro bufite ibitanda 1000, bwageze i New York.
Ku ya 3 Mata, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zahitanye abantu 884 bazize coronavirus mu masaha 24 ashize.
Muri Leta ya New York, umubare w'abanduye warenze 100,000 ku ya 3 Mata. White House yanenzwe kuba yarapfobye ibyago no kugenzura itumanaho mu gutegeka abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu bya siyansi guhuza itangazamakuru n'ibitabo by'ibanze by'iyi virusi n'ibiro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence.
Kwemeranya muri rusange ku buryo Trump yakemuye ikibazo cy'ubukungu byatewe n'amacakubiri ashingiye ku nzego.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Amerika n'abatanga ibitekerezo ku bibazo bya politiki banenze ko Amerika yishingikiriza ku Bushinwa mu birebana no gutumiza ibikoresho by'ingenzi, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi by'ibanze.
Isesengura ry'ingendo z'indege ryakoreshejwe mu gukora amakarita no guhanura ingendo z'ubwandu, kandi ryasohotse mu kinyamakuru cy'ubuvuzi bw'ingendo hagati muri Mutarama 2020.
Dukurikije amakuru yo mu 2018 y'Ishyirahamwe ry'Ubutwererane mu By'Ikirere, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei ni byo by'ingenzi mu ngendo z'indege ziva i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byari ahantu hakunzwe gusurwa n'abantu bavuye i Wuhan.
Bali yagaragaye ko ari wo mujyi wa mbere udashoboye mu mijyi 20 y'ingenzi y'aho abantu bagana mu rwego rwo kwitegura, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Ositaraliya yagaragaye ko ari yo ifite ubushobozi bwo guhangana n'icyorezo. Ositaraliya yashyize ahagaragara gahunda yayo yo guhangana n'icyorezo cya koronavirusi (COVID-19) ku ya 7 Gashyantare.
Yavuze ko hari byinshi bigikeneye kuvumburwa kuri COVID-19 kandi ko Australia izongera ingufu mu gucunga imipaka no gutangaza amakuru mu buryo bwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe, muri Ositaraliya hatangajwe ko habaho ikibazo cy'umutekano w'abantu.
Kubera ko imodoka za rusange zo mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei zaciwe mu kato, ibihugu byinshi byateganyaga gukura abaturage babyo n'abakozi ba dipolomasi muri ako karere, cyane cyane hakoreshejwe indege z'ibihugu by'ibanze, zihawe uburenganzira n'abayobozi b'u Bushinwa.
Canada, Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Australia, Ubufaransa, Argentina, Ubudage na Thailand ni bimwe mu bihugu bya mbere byateguye gahunda yo gucyura abaturage babyo.
Pakistani yavuze ko nta muturage wayo izakura mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Burezili yakuye muri icyo gihugu abaturage 34 b'Abanyabrezili cyangwa abagize imiryango yabo, hamwe n'Abapolonye bane, Umunyashinwa n'Umuhindi umwe.
Abaturage ba Polonye, u Bushinwa n'u Buhinde bageze muri Polonye, aho indege ya Brazil yahagaze mbere yo gukomeza urugendo ijya muri Brezili.
Abaturage ba Brezili bari baragiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato mu kigo cya gisirikare hafi ya Brasília.
Kuri uwo munsi, abantu 215 b'Abanyakanada (176 bari mu ndege ya mbere na 39 bari mu ndege ya kabiri yari yaguze na leta ya Amerika) bavuye i Wuhan bajyanwa muri BFC Trenton kugira ngo bashyirwe mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye Abanyakanada 185 bavuye Wuhan yageze ku kibuga cy'indege cya BFC Trenton.
Abayobozi ba Ositaraliya bakuye abaturage 277 ku ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare, babajyana mu kigo cyo ku kirwa cya Christmas, bahindurwamo ikigo cya karantine, aho bamaze iminsi 14.
Indege yo mu gihugu cya Nouvelle Zelande yageze muri Auckland ku ya 5 Gashyantare; abagenzi bayo (cyane cyane bavuye muri Ositaraliya no muri Pasifika) bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cy'ingabo z'inyanja i Whangaparaoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko zigiye gucyura Abanyamerika bari mu bwato bw'ingendo bwitwa Diamond Princess.
Ku ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abantu 129 b'Abanyakanada bari bavuye mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess yageze i Trenton, Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'u Buhinde yatangiye gucyura abaturage bayo bavuye muri Irani. Ku ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airways yagurijwe na leta ya Afurika y'Epfo yasubije mu gihugu abaturage 112 ba Afurika y'Epfo.
Mbere y'uko berekeza mu mahanga, bapimwe mu bitaro, kandi abantu bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya koronavirusi baguma mu gihugu kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago byo kuyirwara.
Abanyafurika y'Epfo bapimwe basanga nta bwandu bafite ni bo bonyine basubijwe mu gihugu.
Ibisubizo by'ibizamini byahawe abanyafurika y'epfo bose, harimo abakozi bo mu ndege, abashoferi, abakozi bo mu mahoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari mu gikorwa cyo gufasha, bose mu rwego rwo kwirinda, bagumye mu kato no gukurikiranwa mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 muri Ranch Resort.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangiye gukura igice cy'abasirikare bazo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (birimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byohereje imfashanyo mu Bushinwa.
Abanyeshuri b'Abashinwa bake biga muri za kaminuza zo muri Amerika bahurije hamwe kugira ngo bafashe kohereza imfashanyo mu bice by'u Bushinwa byibasiwe n'iyi virusi, itsinda ry'abashyize hamwe ryo mu gace ka Greater Chicago ryatanze udupfukamunwa 50,000 tw'ubwoko bwa N95 ku bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku ya 30 Mutarama. Umuryango utabara imbabare Direct Relief, ufatanyije na FedEx, wohereje udupfukamunwa 200,000 hamwe n'ibindi bikoresho byo kwirinda, harimo uturindantoki n'imyenda yo kwambara, mu ndege yo mu buryo bwihutirwa ku bitaro bya Wuhan Union Hospital ku ya 30 Mutarama.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko bahaye OMS miliyoni 100 z'amadolari yo gushyigikira ubushakashatsi ku rukingo no kwivuza no kurinda abantu bafite ibyago muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Amajyepfo.
Interaksyon yatangaje ko guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa ibihumbi 200 muri Filipine ku ya 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'uko senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, umuryango utabara imbabare wa Singapore Red Cross watangaje ko uzatanga miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu bufasha bw'u Bushinwa.
U Buyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni imwe muri Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, u Burusiya bwohereje toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Wuhan, Maleziya yatangaje ko yatanze imigabane ya miliyoni 18 z'utubumbire two mu buvuzi mu Bushinwa, u Budage bwatanze ibikoresho bitandukanye by'ubuvuzi harimo toni 10,000 z'imyenda y'ubwirinzi, na Amerika yatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa kandi yemeza ko izatanga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari yo gushyigikira ibihugu byugarijwe n'icyorezo. Mu gihe abarwayi bo mu Bushinwa basaga n'aho bahagaze, u Bushinwa bwohereje imfashanyo mu bihugu byinshi byugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'inzobere mu gufasha Ubutaliyani guhangana n'icyorezo cya koronavirusi.
Umushoramari Jack Ma yohereje udukoresho twa serivisi zo gupima virusi miliyoni 1.1, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6 n'imyenda yo kwirinda 60,000 i Addis Ababa muri Etiyopiya kugira ngo ibyo bikoreshwe n'Umuryango wa Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yo kohereza ibikoresho byo gupima 5,000, udupfukamunwa 100,000 n'ibikoresho 5 byo guhumeka muri Panama.
Ma yanatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Kanada. U Buholandi, Espagne, Turukiya, Georgia na Repubulika ya Tchèque bagaragaje impungenge ku masike n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakorewe mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Esipanye yahagaritse ibikoresho 58 000 byo gupima coronavirus byakorewe mu Bushinwa bifite ubuziranenge bwa 30% gusa, mu gihe u Buholandi bwahagaritse udupfukamunwa 600 000 tw'Ubushinwa twari dufite amakosa.
Ububiligi bwasubijeho udupfukamunwa 100.000 tudashobora gukoreshwa; twibwiraga ko ari utwo mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Kolombiya.
Ku rundi ruhande, ubufasha bw'u Bushinwa bwakiriwe neza mu bihugu byo muri Amerika y'Amajyepfo na Afurika.Ku ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije ibikorwa by'ubutabazi bwihutirwa mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimye imbaraga z'abayobozi b'Ubushinwa mu kurwanya no gukumira icyorezo.
OMS yagaragaje itandukaniro riri hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004, aho abayobozi bo mu Bushinwa bashinjwaga guhishira ibyabaye bigatuma ingamba zo gukumira no kurwanya icyorezo zidashoboka, n'iki cyorezo cy'ubu aho guverinoma yo hagati yatanze raporo zisanzwe mu rwego rwo kwirinda ko abantu bagira ubwoba ku munsi w'Ubunani.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu kwitabira icyemezo cy'abayobozi bakuru ba Centrafrika cyo gushyiraho itegeko ryo kubuza abantu kuva mu mujyi wa Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS Gauden Galea yavuze ko nubwo ibyo bitari inama ya OMS, ariko ko byari ikimenyetso gikomeye cyane cy'uko biyemeje guhashya icyorezo aho cyagwiriye cyane, kandi avuga ko ari ikintu kitari cyigeze kibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange. Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ko abantu banduye virusi ya HCoV hanze y'u Bushinwa no kubona umubare w'abantu bayanduye mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo ari icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane mpuzamahanga (USIPPI), mu gihe muri Amerika hashyizweho ingamba zo gukumira icyorezo cya APPI mu mwaka wa 2009.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko USPPI iterwa n'ibyago byo gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amikoro make n'ibifite amikoro yo hagati bidafite inzego z'ubuzima zikomeye.
Mu gusubiza ku iyubahirizwa ry'ibihano ku ngendo, Tedros yagize ati "nta mpamvu n'imwe yatuma ingamba zafashwe zibuza abantu gukora ingendo n'ubucuruzi mpuzamahanga kandi OMS ntishishyigikira ko ingendo n'ubucuruzi byagabanywa".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gufasha ibihugu bifite ubukungu buciriritse kwitegura, ivuga ko byihutirwa gufasha ibihugu "bidashobora kubona uburyo bwo kumenya abantu banduye virusi, nubwo yaba igiye kugaragara".
Tedros yakomeje avuga ko "dufite imbaraga nk'iz'uruhuza rwacu rufite intege nke" kandi asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "kwishora uyu munsi cyangwa kwishyura menshi ejo". Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, OMS mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru, yemeje ko iyi ndwara yitwa COVID-19.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye António Guterres yemeye gushyira imbaraga z'umuryango w'Abibumbye zose mu guhangana n'icyo kibazo.
Ni yo mpamvu itsinda rya LONI rishinzwe kurwanya ibibazo ryafunguwe, rihuza ibikorwa byose by'umuryango w'abibumbye, WHO ivuga ko bizatuma ushyira imbaraga ku gusubiza mu by'ubuzima mu gihe izindi nzego zindi zizatanga ubuhanga bwo gukemura ibibazo by'imibereho, ubukungu n'iterambere by'icyorezo.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda rihuriweho n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangijwe mu Bushinwa kugira ngo rihereze impuguke mpuzamahanga n'iz'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima mu Bushinwa kugira ngo zishyigikire imiyoborere y'igihugu no gusuzuma uburemere n'ikwirakwizwa by'icyorezo binyuze mu gukora amahugurwa n'inama n'inzego z'ibanze z'igihugu no gusura imirenge kugira ngo harebwe ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo kurwanya icyorezo mu ntara no mu byaro, harimo n'ibiri mu mijyi n'ibiturage. Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko isi igomba gukora byinshi mu kwitegura icyorezo cya koronavirusi, rivuga ko nubwo hakiri kare cyane kugira ngo havuge iby'icyorezo, buri gihugu kigomba kwitegura.
Mu gusubiza uko icyorezo cyagendaga gikomera muri Irani, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'abakozi bo muri icyo gihugu kugira ngo barebe uko ibintu byifashe. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS batangaje ko icyorezo cya koronavirusi ku isi cyavuye ku rwego rwo hejuru kikagera ku rwego rwo hejuru, ni ukuvuga ko ari cyo cyateye ubwoba cyane.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru wa gahunda ya OMS yo guhangana n'ibibazo by'ubuzima, yagabishije muri iri tangazo: "Ibi ni ukugaruka ku kuri kuri kuri buri leta ku isi: nimukanguke.
Ashobora kuba ari mu nzira kandi ugomba kwitegura, avuga ko ingamba nziza zo guhangana na yo zishobora gufasha isi kwirinda ibintu bibi cyane.
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru ahari ubu atuma abayobozi b'ubuzima bw'abaturage batatangaza ko ari icyorezo ku isi, avuga ko gutangaza ko ari icyorezo bivuze ko "twemera rwose ko buri muntu ku isi ashobora kuba ahanganye n'iyi virusi".
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya koronavirusi gishobora kwitwa icyorezo.
Umuyobozi mukuru yavuze ko OMS ihangayikishijwe cyane n'uburyo iyi ndwara ikwirakwizwa kandi ikabije ndetse n'uburyo idakora. OMS yagezweho n'ibihano bikomeye bijyanye n'uburyo yayigenzuraga, ibivugwa ko itari ihagije, cyane cyane kubera gutinda gutangaza ko ari ikibazo cy'ubuzima rusange cy'ingutu no gushyira virusi ku rutonde rw'indwara y'icyorezo.
Ibyo byemezo bivuye inyuma byashyigikiwe n'inyandiko y'ubusabe yasabaga Umuyobozi wa OMS Tedros Adhanom kwegura, yari imaze gusinywa n'abantu 733.000 ku ya 6 Mata.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, inzobere nyinshi mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu mu muryango w'abibumbye zashimangiye ko uburenganzira bwa buri muntu bugomba kubahirizwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Inteko y'impuguke yavuze ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo guhabwa ubufasha bw'ibanze kandi ko ari inshingano ya leta.
Iryo tsinda ryanashimangiye ko kubura amikoro cyangwa ubwisungane mu kwivuza bitagomba na rimwe kuba impamvu yo kurobanura ku butoni ku itsinda runaka.
Abahanga bagaragaje ko buri muntu afite uburenganzira ku buzima, harimo abafite ubumuga, abo mu moko make, abageze mu za bukuru, abimukira, abatagira aho baba, abafite ubukene bukabije, abafunzwe, impunzi n'andi matsinda adasobanutse akeneye inkunga ya leta.
Amashyirahamwe mpuzamahanga ya leta arimo arakora ku ngaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage ziterwa n'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Ibihugu by'Ubukungu n'Iterambere watangije urubuga rutanga amakuru ajyanye n'igihe kandi yuzuye ku bisubizo bya politiki mu bihugu bitandukanye ku isi, ndetse n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Hagati ya politiki zo gukomeza gahunda z'ubuzima n'ubukungu bw'isi no guhangana n'ingaruka zo gufunga no kugabanya ingendo, urubuga rwa interineti rurimo igikoresho cya Country Policy Tracker kigamije gufasha ibihugu kwigirana no koroshya uburyo bwo guhangana n'ikibazo cya koronavirusi ku isi hose.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yanenzwe na Amerika, Minisitiri w'Abongereza mu biro by'abaminisitiri Michael Gove n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Brezili Jair Bolsonaro, Eduardo Bolsonaro, kubera uburyo ayobora icyorezo cyaturutse mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Abayobozi benshi bo mu Nteko y'Abakomunisiti mu Bushinwa (CCP) bakuwe ku mirimo yabo nyuma yo gucunga gahunda yo gushyira abantu mu kato mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, mu buryo bugaragara ko hari ukunanirwa kw'abayobozi mu rwego rwa politiki mu guhangana n'icyorezo muri utwo turere.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bavuga ko icyo gikorwa cyabaye mu rwego rwo kurinda Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka rya Komini ry'Abashinwa Xi Jinping uburakari bw'abaturage kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi bakuru b'u Bushinwa, nka Zhao Lijian, banze igitekerezo cya mbere cy'uko icyorezo cya koronavirusi cyatangiriye i Wuhan, bahitamo ibitekerezo by'uko COVID-19 yakomotse muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
