Icyorezo cya koronavirusi cyagaragaye ko cyateje ibibazo byinshi by'ibura ry'ibicuruzwa, bitewe n'ubwiyongere bw'isi yose mu gukoresha ibikoresho byo kurwanya icyorezo, kugura ibintu mu buryo butunguranye no guhagarika inganda no gukora ibikorwa byo gutanga ibikoresho.
Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika gishinzwe ibiryo n'imiti cyatanze imiburo ku bijyanye n'ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitewe n'ubwiyongere bw'abakiliya n'ibura ry'abatanga ibicuruzwa.
Mu duce twinshi, abantu baguze ibintu mu buryo bwo gutinya ko bishobora kubacika, bituma ibintu by'ibanze nk'ibiribwa, impapuro z'isuku n'amacupa y'amazi biva ku meza bigatangira kubura, bigatuma habaho ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibikoresho.
Ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga, by'umwihariko, cyatangaje ko ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga byatinze koherezwa.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko umubare w'ibikoresho birinda umuntu ku giti cye byifuzwa wiyongereyeho inshuro 100.
Ibyo byateje izamuka ry'ibiciro inshuro zigera kuri 20 z'ibiciro bisanzwe kandi byateje n'izamuka ry'ibiciro by'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu gihe cy'amezi ane kugeza kuri atandatu.
Ibi kandi byatumye habaho ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibikoresho byo kwikingira ku isi hose, kandi OMS iravuga ko ibyo bizashyira mu kaga abakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima.
Muri Ositaraliya, icyorezo cy'icyorezo cyabahaye amahirwe mashya yo kugurisha ibicuruzwa by'Abanyamerika mu Bushinwa.
Iyi mikorere yatumye habaho ikibazo cy'ibura ry'amata y'abana mu masoko amwe n'amwe, nyuma yaho leta ya Ositaraliya irahagarika. Nubwo hari abantu benshi banduye COVID-19 mu majyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani no mu karere ka Wuhan, ndetse n'ibura ry'ibiribwa ryaje gukurikirwa n'ibyo bibazo, utwo duce twombi ntitwabonywe ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibiribwa.
Ingamba zafashwe n'Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani zo kurwanya ububiko n'ubucuruzi bw'ibikoresho by'ibanze mu buryo butemewe n'amategeko byaranzwe n'ibyishimo, bituma habaho ibura ry'ibiribwa ryari ryitezwe mu Burayi no muri Amerika y'Amajyaruguru.
Kubera umusaruro munini w'ubuhinzi, mu majyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani nta kugabanuka gukomeye kwabayeho, ariko ibiciro bishobora kwiyongera nk'uko abahagarariye inganda babivuga.
Amashashi y'ibiribwa yari amaze igihe gito gusa atunganyirijwe ubusa, ndetse no mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu gihe abayobozi ba leta y'Ubushinwa bari bamaze gufungura ibiribwa by'ingurube kugira ngo abaturage babone ibibatunga.
Mu Butaliyani, hari amategeko nk'ayo, kugira ngo aborozi b'ibiribwa bajye babika ibyo bazakenera mu gihe hazabaho ibyo bibazo by'impanuka.
Ingaruka mbi ku bukungu bw'isi zabaye mu Bushinwa: nk'uko byatangajwe n'ibinyamakuru ku ya 16 Werurwe, ubukungu bw'Ubushinwa bwarazahajwe cyane mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020 kubera ingamba za leta zo gukumira ikwirakwizwa rya virusi, kandi ibicuruzwa ku isoko byamanutseho 20,5%.
Kubera ko Ubushinwa bw'ibanze ari ihuriro rikomeye ry'ubukungu n'ubwikorezi, byagaragaye ko icyorezo cya virusi ari cyo kibangamiye cyane ubukungu bw'isi.
Agathe Demarais wo mu kigo cy'ubutasi cy'Umutunzi, yavuze ko amasoko azakomeza guhungabana kugeza igihe hazaba hari isura isobanutse y'uko ibintu bizagenda.
Muri Mutarama 2020, abahanga mu by'ubukungu bavuze ko ingaruka z'ubukungu z'icyorezo ku iterambere ry'isi zishobora kurenga iz'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004.
Umushakashatsi wo muri Kaminuza ya Washington iri i St. Louis, yavuze ko ingaruka z'ubucuruzi ku isoko ry'ibicuruzwa ku isi zishobora kuba zirenga miriyari 300 z'amadolari, kandi ko zishobora kumara imyaka ibiri.
Umuryango w'ibihugu bitumiza peteroli (OPEC) byatangaje ko wagize ikibazo nyuma y'igabanuka rikomeye ry'ibiciro bya peteroli bitewe n'uko ubukungu bw'Ubushinwa bwagabanutse.
Ku wa 24 Gashyantare, amasoko y'imari n'imari ku isi yagabanutse bitewe n'ubwiyongere bw'abanduye COVID-19 hanze y'Ubushinwa.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, kubera impungenge z'uko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyugarije Amerika, ibipimo by'ibicuruzwa byinshi byo muri Amerika birimo NASDAQ-100, S&amp;P 500 na Dow Jones Industrial Average byaguye cyane kuva mu 2008, Dow Jones igera ku 1.191 ku munsi umwe, ari na cyo cyanze guhita kuva mu gihe cy'ihungabana ry'imari ryo mu 2007-08.
Ibipimo by'ibiciro bitatu byose byarangiye icyumweru bimanutseho hejuru ya 10%.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, Scope Ratings GmbH yemeje igipimo cy'umwenda w'igihugu cy'Ubushinwa, ariko igumana icyizere cyo kutagenda neza.
Ibiciro byongeye kugwa kubera ubwoba bw'icyorezo cya koronavirusi, aho ku ya 16 Werurwe ari bwo byagabanutse cyane.
Abantu benshi batekereza ko ubukungu bushobora kuzamo agatotsi.
Umuhanga mu by'ubukungu, Mohamed El-Erian yashimye ingamba zihutirwa zashyizweho mu gihe gikwiriye n'amabanki makuru n'ibihugu.
Banki nkuru z'ibihugu zirimo kwihuta cyane mu guhangana n'ikibazo cy'ihungabana ry'ubukungu ry'umwaka wa 2008.
Ubukerarugendo ni kimwe mu by'ingenzi byibasiwe n'ibihano byo gufunga ibikorwa rusange, harimo n'iby'ubukerarugendo, n'amabwiriza ya za leta abuza abantu kujya mu bindi bihugu.
Ibi byatumye kompanyi nyinshi z'indege zihagarika ingendo kubera ko abantu batagikeneye gukora cyane, zirimo British Airways, China Eastern Airlines na Qantas, mu gihe kompanyi y'indege y'akarere yo mu Bwongereza ya Flybe yavuye mu isambu.
Ingaruka ku ngendo zo mu nyanja zageze ku rwego rutarigeze rubaho mbere.
Hari n'ibibuga by'indege n'iby'indege byafunzwe.
Iki cyorezo cyagaragaye mu gihe cya Chunyun, igihe gikomeye cy'ubukerarugendo gihuriweho n'Ubunani.
Ibikorwa byinshi by'abantu benshi byahagaritswe na za leta n'intara, harimo n'ibirori ngarukamwaka byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya, kandi n'ibigo by'abikorera ku giti cyabo na byo byafunze amaduka n'ahantu nyaburanga nk'ahitwa Hong Kong Disneyland na Shanghai Disneyland.
Ibirori byinshi bijyanye n'Umwaka Mushya w'Abanyekwezi byakuweho, kandi ahantu henshi hakurura ba mukerarugendo hafungiwe abantu benshi, harimo Umujyi Utagenewe i Beijing n'ibirori by'urusengero.
Mu ntara 24 muri 31 z'Ubushinwa, abategetsi b'uturere n'uturere, batanze amabwiriza yo kongera iminsi y'ikiruhuko y'Ubunani kugeza ku ya 10 Gashyantare, maze basaba ko amazu menshi y'akazi atazongera gufungura mbere y'iyo tariki.
Ibihugu by'ibituranyi byagize 80% by'umusaruro mbumbe w'igihugu na 90% by'ibyoherezwa hanze.
Hong Kong yafashe ingamba zihuse zo guhangana n'indwara zandura kandi itangaza ko hari ikibazo cyihutirwa, ifunga amashuri kugeza muri Werurwe, kandi ikareka kwizihiza umunsi mukuru w'umwaka mushya. Uruganda rw'ubucuruzi ku isi yose rwagize ingaruka, aho usanga amaduka yagabanyijwe amasaha yo gufungura cyangwa afungwa by'agateganyo.
Kujya mu bacuruzi mu Burayi no muri Amerika y'Epfo byagabanutseho 40%.
Mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati no muri Amerika ya Ruguru, abacuruzi babonye ko bari kugabanutseho hagati ya 50 na 60 ku ijana.
Byatumye kandi imodoka zica hagati ya 33 na 43 ku ijana mu rugendo rw'amaguru mu masoko mu kwezi kwa gatatu ugereranyije n'uko byari bimeze muri Gashyantare.
Abashinzwe amaduka ku isi hose bashyizeho ingamba z'inyongera, zirimo kongera umubare w'abakora isuku, gushyiraho ibyuma bifata ubushyuhe kugira ngo bigenzure ubushyuhe bw'abakiliya no guhagarika ibikorwa. Komisiyo y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ishinzwe ubukungu muri Amerika y'Amajyepfo igaragaza ko icyorezo cy'icyorezo gishobora gutuma abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 14 na 22 muri Amerika y'Amajyepfo baba mu bukene bukabije ugereranyije n'igihe kitari icyorezo.
Muri Mutarama na Gashyantare 2020, igihe icyorezo cyari cyakwiriye cyane mu mujyi wa Wuhan, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 5 mu Bushinwa batakaje akazi.
Mu Bushinwa, benshi mu bakozi bo mu cyaro bagera kuri miliyoni 300 bari mu ngendo, baguye mu rugo mu ntara zo hagati mu gihugu cyangwa baguye mu ntara ya Hubei. Muri Werurwe 2020, Abanyamerika barenga miliyoni 10 batakaje akazi maze basaba leta ubufasha.
Icyorezo cya koronavirusi gishobora gutwara imirimo miliyoni 47 muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, n'umubare w'abashomeri ushobora kugera kuri 32%, nk'uko bigaragazwa n'ikigo cy'imari cy'ibanze cya St. Louis. Gahunda yo guhagarika mu Buhinde yatumye abakozi b'abimukira bo mu Buhinde babarirwa muri za miriyoni (bahembwa ku munsi) babura akazi. Iperereza ryakozwe n'ikigo cya Angus Reid ryagaragaje ko 44% by'ingo zo muri Kanada zari zarahuye n'ubushomeri. Abakozi bagera hafi ku 900 000 batakaje akazi muri Esipanye kuva igihe cyo guhagarika ibikorwa by'akazi gitangiwe hagati ya Werurwe 2020.
Mu gice cya kabiri cy'ukwezi kwa Werurwe, abakozi miliyoni 4 bo mu Bufaransa basabye inguzanyo y'ubushomeri bw'igihe gito, naho abakozi miliyoni 1 bo mu Bwongereza basabye inguzanyo rusange.Abagera hafi kuri miliyoni imwe bo mu bigo byo mu Budage bahinduye abakozi babo bajya mu buryo bwo gukora igihe gito bufashwa na leta bwitwa Kurzarbeit.
Gahunda y'Ubudage yo guhemba abakozi bakora igihe gito yemeye ubufatanye bw'Ubufaransa n'Ubwongereza.
Urwego rw'ubuhanzi n'umurage ndangamuco byagizweho ingaruka zikomeye n'icyorezo, bigira ingaruka ku mikorere y'imiryango n'abantu ku giti cyabo, baba abakora ku giti cyabo n'abikorera ku isi hose.
Imiryango y'ubuhanzi n'umuco yagerageje gukomeza inshingano zayo (akenshi zishyurwa na Leta) mu gutanga uburyo bwo kugera ku murage ndangamuco w'abaturage, kurinda umutekano w'abakozi bayo n'abaturage no gushyigikira abahanzi aho bishoboka.
Muri Werurwe 2020, hirya no hino ku isi, mu byiciro bitandukanye, amazu ndangamurage, ibitabo, amareresi n'ibindi bigo by'umuco byafunzwe kugeza igihe habonekeye andi mabwiriza, imurikabikorwa, ibirori n'imikino byigijwe inyuma cyangwa byarahagaritswe.
Mu gusubiza, hashyizweho ingamba zikomeye zo gutanga serivisi z'inyongera binyuze mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga. Ikindi cyemezo giherutse no kwihutishwa n'iki cyorezo, ni uguhagarika ibikorwa by'idini, ibirori bikomeye by'imikino n'ibindi bikorwa rusange, nk'ibirori by'umuziki n'ibitaramo, inama z'ikoranabuhanga n'imurikabikorwa ry'imideri.
Isosiyete y'amafilimi na yo yahagaritswe, Vatican itangaza ko ibirori byo kwizihiza icyumweru gitagatifu i Roma, bizaba mu cyumweru cya nyuma cy'igihe cy'ububabare bw'abakristo mu gihe cy'igisibo cya Misa, byahagaritswe.
Diyoseze nyinshi zasabye abakristo bageze mu za bukuru kuguma mu ngo zabo aho kujya mu misa ku cyumweru; amadini amwe akwirakwiza amateraniro yayo kuri radiyo, kuri interineti no kuri televiziyo, mu gihe andi atangira gukorera mu modoka.
Kimwe na Diyosezi Gatolika ya Roma yafunze insengero zayo n'insengero ntoya zayo, na St. Peter's Square yakuwemo abakirisitu bayo bose, andi madini na yo yahagaritse ibikorwa byayo kandi agabanya amateraniro rusange mu nsengero, imisigiti, amasengero, insengero n'ahantu ho gusengera.
Minisitiri w'ubuzima wa Irani yatangaje ko amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu mu duce twibasiwe n'icyorezo yahagaritswe, nyuma n'ahantu hatagatifu harafungwa, mu gihe Arabiya Sawudite yabujije abanyamahanga n'abaturage bayo kwinjira mu duce twera twa Mecca na Medina.
