Gukora isuzuma muri laboratwari ry'indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) na virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 bifitanye isano, bikubiyemo uburyo bwo kumenya virusi no kumenya abasirikare b'umubiri bavutse mu gihe umuntu yanduye.
Kugira virusi mu bipimo byemezwa na RT-PCR, igaragaza ko hari virusi ya koronavirusi.
Iyi porogaramu yagenewe by'umwihariko gusesengura SARS-CoV-2 RNA gusa.
Ikoreshwa mu kwemeza ko umuntu aherutse kwandura cyangwa ko hari undi muntu ukirwaye.
Gukoresha uburyo bwo gupima abasirikare b'umubiri (serologie) bishobora gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma no kugenzura abantu.
Ibizamini by'umubiri bigaragaza umubare w'abantu banduye, harimo n'abantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje ku buryo bitavugwa, cyangwa se n'abatabyerekanye.
Ibipimo by'umubare w'abapfa n'uwanduye n'uburyo ubwirinzi bw'ubwoko bw'abantu bushobora kumenyekana hakoreshejwe ibizamini by'ubu bushakashatsi.
Kubera ko ibipimo by'ibipimo byari bike, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku bijyanye n'uko virusi yageze mu baturage muri Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari kimaze gupima abaturage bangana na 3% by'abaturage bacyo, kandi hari itandukaniro rinini ry'umubare w'abapimwe muri buri gihugu.
Birashoboka ko iri hinduka rigira ingaruka zikomeye ku bipimo by'impfu, bishobora kurenza cyane ibipimo by'impfu mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Gukoresha uburyo bwo gupima hakurikijwe uburyo bwa rRT-PCR (Reverse Transcription followed by Real-Time Polymerization Chain Reaction), ibipimo by' umwuka bishobora gukorwa hifashishijwe uburyo butandukanye, harimo gukoresha uburyo bwo gupima mu mazuru cyangwa mu kanwa.
Ibisubizo bikunze kuboneka mu masaha make kugeza ku minsi 2.
Ibizamini bya RT-PCR bikorerwa ku bipfunsi by'utugingo byiringirwa gusa mu cyumweru cya mbere cy'indwara.
Nyuma y'aho, virusi ishobora guhera mu muhogo ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha.
Ku bantu banduye bapimwa mu cyumweru cya kabiri, hashobora gukurwaho icyuma mu myanya y'ubuhumekero mu buryo bw'imashini, cyangwa hakoreshwa amacandwe.
Kimwe mu bizamini bya mbere bya PCR cyakozwe na Charité i Berlin muri Mutarama 2020 hifashishijwe uburyo bw'ubwandukuzi bw'inyuguti z'inyuranyo (rRT-PCR), kandi cyabaye ishingiro ry'ibikoresho 250 000 byatanzwe n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO).
Ubwongereza nabwo bwari bwarakoze ikizamini ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020. Ikigo cyo muri Koreya y'Epfo cya Kogenebiotech cyakoze ibikoresho byo gupima SARS-CoV-2 bikoreshwa mu buvuzi bushingiye kuri PCR (PowerChek Coronavirus) ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020.
