Gukaraba intoki, nanone bita isuku y'intoki, ni ugukaraba intoki kugira ngo ukureho imyanda, amavuta, udukoko duto cyangwa ibindi bintu bidakenewe.
Gukaraba intoki buri gihe ukoresheje isabune mu "bihe by'ingenzi" by'umunsi, birinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'indwara y'ubuhumekero na kolera, zanduzwa n'imyanda yo mu kanwa.
Birashoboka ko umuntu yandura indwara z'ubuhumekero nka grippe cyangwa se ibicurane, urugero, iyo umuntu yanze gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, ku zuru cyangwa ku munwa (ni ukuvuga ku matembabuzi).
Ni ngombwa gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu bihe bitanu by'ingenzi by'umunsi: mbere na nyuma yo gukorora, nyuma yo gukaraba umwana cyangwa kumusubiza ibitambaro, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya na mbere na nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gukora ku nyama, ifi cyangwa inkoko itaratunganywa.
Niba udafite isabune n'amazi, ushobora gukaraba intoki ukoresheje umwanda. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) ryifuza gukaraba intoki:
mbere, mu gihe no nyuma yo gutegura amafunguro;
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku muntu urwaye;
Nyuma yo guhindura umwana ibyokurya cyangwa gukubura umwana wagiye mu bwiherero
Nyuma yo kwitsamura cyangwa gukorora/kwitsamura;
Nyuma yo gukora ku nyamaswa, ku biribwa by'inyamaswa cyangwa ku myanda y'inyamaswa,
Isuku y'intoki mu buvuzi yerekeza ku bikorwa by'isuku bijyana n'uburyo bwo kwivuza.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gutanga imiti cyangwa kwivuza bishobora gukumira cyangwa kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Intego y'ibanze mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi yo gukaraba intoki ni ukuvanaho indwara (bakiteri, virusi n'utundi dukoko duto dushobora guteza indwara) n'imiti ishobora guteza indwara.
Iyi myitozo ni ingenzi cyane ku bantu bakora mu by'ibiribwa cyangwa bakora mu by'ubuvuzi, ariko no ku bantu muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kanini ku buzima, harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ibicurane, koronavirusi n'izindi ndwara z'ibyorezo; kwirinda indwara zandura zitera diyabete; kugabanya indwara zo mu buhumekero;
ndetse no kugabanya igipimo cy'abana bapfa mu gihe babyarira iwabo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2013 bwagaragaje ko kugira isuku yo mu ntoki nziza bishobora gutuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu barushaho gukura neza.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, umubare w'abana bicwa n'indwara z'ubuhumekero n'impiswi ushobora kugabanuka hifashishijwe impinduka zoroheje mu myitwarire, nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Uku gukora ibintu byoroheje bishobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa bitewe n'iyo ndwara ku kigero cya 50%.
Gushyiraho ingamba zo gukangurira abantu gukaraba intoki bishobora kugabanya ibyago by'impiswi ku kigero cya kimwe cya gatatu, ibi bikaba bingana n'ibyagerwaho mu kugeza amazi meza mu turere dufite amikoro make.
Gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe isabune bigabanya 48% by'indwara z'iseru, kandi ni bwo buryo bwiza kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda iseru n'indwara z'ubuhumekero (RAI). Ni igikorwa kigomba gukorwa mu buryo bwikora mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu mibereho ku isi hose.
Indwara y'ibihaha, imwe mu ndwara z'ibyorezo zikomeye, ni yo ndwara y'ibanze yica abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu, ihitana abagera hafi kuri miliyoni 1,8 buri mwaka.
Iyo mibare yose hamwe, iseru n'indwara y'ibihaha bihitana abana bagera kuri miliyoni 3,5 buri mwaka.
UNICEF ivuga ko kugira akamenyero ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mbere yo kurya na nyuma yo kuva mu bwiherero bishobora kurokora ubuzima bw'abantu benshi kurusha urukingo urwo ari rwo rwose cyangwa ubuvuzi ubwo ari bwo bwose, kandi bikagabanya hafi kimwe cya kabiri cy'abapfa bazize indwara z'impiswi, ndetse n'igice cya kane cy'abapfa bazize indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Gukaraba intoki bikunze gukorana n'izindi ngamba z'isuku mu rwego rwa gahunda z'amazi, isuku n'isuku (WASH).
Nanone gukaraba intoki birinda indwara ya impyiko, yandura binyuze mu guhura n'umuntu.
Ingaruka nke cyane, gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora kwangiza uruhu, bigatuma ruba rwumye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe muri Danemark mu 2012 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutera indwara y'uruhu n'indwara y'uruhu, aho umuntu agira uruhu rw'uruhu rwijimye kandi rukamurika, kandi bikaba bikunze kugaragara cyane mu bakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki cyane na byo bifatwa nk'ikimenyetso kimwe cy'indwara y'igwingira (OCD).
Ni ngombwa gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune mu bihe bitanu by'ingenzi by'umunsi mu kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara mu kanwa no mu myanya y'ibanga: mbere na nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero (gukorora, gusohora), nyuma yo gukaraba umwana ibisebe (cyangwa guhindura ibisebe), mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya na mbere na nyuma yo gutegura ibiribwa cyangwa gukorana n'inyama, ifi cyangwa inkoko zitari mbisi.
Nanone kandi, gukaraba intoki neza ni ngombwa kugira ngo umuntu arinde kwandura indwara, cyane cyane mbere na nyuma yo kuvura igisebe cyangwa igikomere, nyuma yo kwitsamura, gukorora cyangwa kwipfuna, nyuma yo gukora ku myanda y'inyamaswa cyangwa gukora ku nyamaswa, na nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, umubare w'abantu bakoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki ni muto.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2015 ku gihugu 54 ku isuku y'intoki, bwagaragaje ko ku kigereranyo cy'ingo 38,7% bakoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki. Ubushakashatsi bwo mu 2014 bwagaragaje ko muri Arabiya Sawudite ari ho umubare wari hejuru cyane (97%), muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika ni hagati (77%) naho mu Bushinwa ni ho umubare uri hasi (23%) Ubu hari uburyo butandukanye bwo guhindura imyitwarire no gukoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki mu bihe by'ingenzi by'umunsi. Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, uburyo bushobora gukorwa ni ugusaba abanyeshuri gukorana mu matsinda mu gihe runaka cy'umunsi kugira ngo abana babashe kubikora.
