Mu mpera z'imyaka ya 1990 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, imiti yo gukaraba intoki idafite amazi ikoreshwa mu gusukura intoki (bakunze kuyita hydroalcoholic solutions, antiseptic solutions cyangwa hand sanitizers) yatangiye gukundwa.
Byinshi byakozwe hifashishijwe isopropyl alcohol cyangwa ethanol ifatanyije n'ikinyabutabire nka carbomere (polymer ya acrylic acid) kugirango haboneke gel, cyangwa humidifiers nka glycerine kugirango haboneke amazi cyangwa isupu kugirango byoroshye gukoresha no kugabanya ingaruka zo gukama kw'inzoga.
