Imiti yica udukoko twanduza virusi, uducurama twanduza virusi (SARM na ERV), igituntu na virusi zimwe na zimwe (harimo virusi itera sida, herpes, RSV, rhinovirus, urukingo, ibicurane na hepatite) ndetse na fungus.
