Imiti y'amazi n'ibinyobwa ni ingirakamaro cyane mu kurwanya virusi zo mu bwoko bwa norovirus (cyangwa Norwalk), ari yo ntandaro y'indwara y'urwungano ngogozi. Hakwiye gukoreshwa umuti uhagije wo gukaraba intoki cyangwa umuti w'amazi n'ibinyobwa kugira ngo bihumeke neza cyangwa bitwikire ibiganza byombi.
