Uburyo bwo kugenzura ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19 ku kazi
Igenzura ry'ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19 ku kazi rivuga gushyira mu bikorwa uburyo bwo kubungabunga ubuzima n'umutekano ku kazi mu rwego rwo kugenzura ibyago byo kwandura indwara ya koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-19).
Uburyo bwo kwirinda indwara bukwiriye mu kazi butandukana bitewe n'aho umuntu ari n'imirimo akora, hashingiwe ku gusuzuma ibyago byo kwandura, ku buremere bw'indwara mu baturage no ku bintu bishobora guteza COVID-19 ku bakozi.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'Ikigo gishinzwe ubuzima n'umutekano ku kazi (OSHA) muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, akazi gashobora guteza ibyago bike cyane ni akazi gafite aho umuntu agera gake cyane mu baturage n'abandi bakozi. Muri ibyo bikorwa, hakoreshwa gusa ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura, zirimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, kwirinda guhumeka no gukora isuku isanzwe no guhumeka ahantu bakorera.
Imirimo ishobora gutuma umuntu yandura mu buryo bworoshye ni iy'abantu bahora bahura cyangwa bahura n'abantu badafite COVID-19 cyangwa ngo bakeka ko bayanduye, ariko bashobora kuba bayanduye kubera ko bakwirakwije mu baturage cyangwa se bagiye mu mahanga.
Ibyo bikubiyemo abakozi bahura n'abaturage, cyane cyane mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwamo imirimo huzuye abantu benshi, ndetse no mu duce tumwe na tumwe bacuruza ibintu byinshi.
Uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura, ingamba zo kwirinda ibyago muri iri tsinda zirimo gukoresha uburyo bwo guhumeka neza hakoreshejwe ibikoresho byangiza umwuka, amadirishya y'isuku no gukoresha ibikoresho byo kwikingira mu gihe uhuye n'umuntu ufite COVID-19.
LOSHA ibona ko abantu bakora mu nzego z'ubuzima n'iz'ihamba bakorana n'abantu bakekwaho cyangwa bazwiho kuba barwaye COVID-19 bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, bikazamuka bikajya ku rwego rwo hejuru cyane mu gihe bakora ibikorwa byo gukora isuku cyangwa gufata cyangwa gukorana n'abantu bakekwaho cyangwa bazwiho kuba barwaye COVID-19.
