WHO ivuga ko kwambara agapfukamunwa ko mu gihe cyo kubaga byemewe gusa n'abakozi bakora mu rwego rwo gupima abantu ku mupaka.
Ku bantu bakusanya ibipimo by'ubuhumekero, kwita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 cyangwa kubajyana mu modoka badafite uburyo bwo kubaga butanga umwuka, OMS itera inkunga ko bambara agapfukamunwa gakoreshwa mu kubaga, amadarubindi cyangwa agakingirizo, ikoti n'utubambaro tw'intoki.
Iyo habaho ibikorwa byo gutera umwuka, agapfukamunwa gakoreshwa mu kubaga gasimbuzwa agapfukamunwa ko mu bwoko bwa N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Kubera ko ku isi hose hataboneka ibikoresho bihagije byo kwikingira, OMS isaba ko hakenerwa koroshya ikoreshwa ry'imiti yo kwikingira hakoreshejwe uburyo bwa telemedicine, gushyiraho inzitizi z'umubiri nk'amadirisha asukuye, kugabanya abantu binjira mu cyumba cy'umurwayi wa COVID-19 bakageneraho abantu bashinzwe kwitabwaho, gukoresha ibikoresho byo kwikingira bikenewe gusa mu gihe hari igikorwa runaka, gukoresha agapfukamunwa kamwe mu buryo buhoraho ariko ntibikureho mu gihe urwaye abarwayi benshi bafite ikibazo kimwe, kugenzura no guhuza ibikorwa byo gukingira no kwikingira hakoreshejwe ibikoresho byo kwikingira no kubuza abantu batagaragaza ibimenyetso gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
