Enzyme ihindura angiotensin 2 (ACE2) ni enzyme ifitanye isano n'uruhande rwo hanze (imyanda y'ingirabuzima) y'ingirabuzima z'ibihaha, mu mitsi, umutima, impyiko n'intanga.
LACE2 ikora ku buryo bw'imikorere ya angio-conversion enzyme (ACE) igabanya ingano ya angio-conversion enzyme II kandi ikongera Ang (1-7) bigatuma iba umuti wizewe mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. LACE2 ni n'aho yinjira mu ngirabuzima za virusi zimwe na zimwe za koronavirusi.
Ubwoko bwa enzyme mu bantu bwitwa hACE2.
Iyi enzymu ihindura angiotensin 2 ni metalloenzyme irimo zinc iri ku bice by'imbere mu mubiri no ku bindi bice by'umubiri.
ACE2 ifite igice cya M2 cya peptidase gifite iherezo rya N n'igice cya collectrine gifite iherezo rya C.
LACE2 ni poroteyine ya poroteyine yo mu bwoko bwa I ifite inzira imwe gusa, ifite ahantu ikora nk'imikorere y'imikorere y'imikorere yerekanwa ku ruhu rw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ibihaha n'izindi ngingo.
Akarere ka extracellular ka lACE2 gatandukanywa n'akarere ka transmembrane na andi ma-enzymes yitwa sheddase; poroteyine ishyirwa mu maraso ikavamo ikajya mu maraso hanyuma ikajya mu musarane.
LACE2 iboneka mu ngingo hafi ya zose: LACE2 ifatanyije n'urwungano rw'ingirabuzima fatizo cyane cyane mu misemburo y'ibihaha ya alveoli yo mu bwoko bwa II, mu misemburo yo mu mara mato, mu misemburo y'amaraso yo mu mitsi no mu mitsi yo mu mitsi yo mu mitsi yo mu bice byinshi by'umubiri.
Ibonekerwa rya lACE2 lRNA risanzwe kandi mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubwonko kiri mu nzira, mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa hypothalamus no mu gice cy'ubwonko.
Igikorwa cy'ibanze cya ACE2 ni ugufasha ACE.
Ivuriro rya ACE ribangurira mu buryo bw'ibinyabutabire, rigahindura angiotensin I muri angiotensin II.
LACE2 nayo igabanya acide aminé phénylamine ifite iherezo rya carboxyle ya angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) ikayihinduramo angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
LACE2 ishobora kandi gutandukanya indi peptides nyinshi harimo [des-Arg9]-bradykinine, lapelin, neurotensin, dynorphine A, na ghrelin.
LACE2 kandi igenga ubwandu bw'imyanda bw'umuyoboro utanga aside ya amine SLC6A19 kandi ifitanye isano n'indwara ya Hartnup.
Kubera ko ACE2 ari poroteyine y'uruhu, ni yo nzira y'ibanze ya virusi za koronavirusi zimwe zinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo, harimo HCoV-NL63, SARS-CoV (virusi itera SARS) na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi itera COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, guhuza poroteyine ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 ya S1 n'agace k'ingirabuzima fatizo ya ACE2 ku isura y'ingirabuzima fatizo bituma habaho endositosisi no kwimurwa kw'iyo virusi na poroteyine mu gice cy'imbere cy'ingirabuzima.
Iyi nzira yo kwinjira mu mubiri isaba kandi ko poroteyine S ihabwa imbaraga na serine protease TMPRSS2, ubu ikaba iri gukorwaho ubushakashatsi kugira ngo ihagarikwe nk'uburyo bwo kuvura. Ibi bituma bamwe batekereza ko kugabanya urugero rwa ACE2 mu mubiri bishobora gufasha kurwanya ubwandu.
Ariko kandi, imiryango myinshi y'inzobere mu by'ubuvuzi n'inzego z'ubugenzuzi zasabye ko hakomeza gukurikizwa uburyo busanzwe bwo kuvura hakoreshejwe imiti igabanya ubukana bwa ACE na ARB.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe kandi bwakozwe bwageze ku itegurwa ry'ibisubizo ryasohowe ku ya 11 Nyakanga 2012 ryagaragaje ko  gukoresha ACEs byajyaniranaga no kugabanya cyane 34% ibyago byo kurwara umusonga ugereranyije n'abagenzuzi. 
Byongeye kandi, ibyago byo kurwara umusonga na byo byagabanutse ku barwayi bafashe ACE inhibitor bari bafite ibyago byo kurwara umusonga, cyane cyane abafashwe n' uburwayi bwo mu bwonko n' umutima.
Gukoresha ACE inhibitors byongeyeho kugabanuka kw'impfu zituruka kuri pneumonia, n'ubwo ibisubizo byari bike ugereranyije n'ibyavuye mu kwibasirwa na pneumonia muri rusange. 
Igisubizo cya human recombinant angiotensin 2 enzyme conversion enzyme (rhACE2) kirimo gukoreshwa nk' umuti mushya mu kuvura indwara zikomeye z'ibihaha kandi gisa n' gitanga umusaruro mu buryo bwo kongera umuvuduko w'amaraso mu bihaha no kongera umwuka mwiza mu ngurube zifite ikibazo cy'ubuhumekero (ARDS) buterwa na lipopolysaccharide.
Igice cy' igihe cyo kubaho cya rhACE2 mu bantu ni hafi amasaha 10 kandi igihe cyo gukora ni iminota 30 ukongeraho igihe cyo gukora (igihe) cy' amasaha 24.
Bimwe mu byavuye mu bushakashatsi byerekana ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti w' icyizere ku bantu batakwihanganira imiti ya kera ya renin-angiotensin system (RAS) cyangwa indwara ziganjemo angiotensin II. rhACE2 yavuye mu maraso yagenzurwaga mu bushakashatsi bw' ibipimo byo kuvura indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Porogaramu za COVID-19 ni porogaramu zikoreshwa kuri telefoni zigamije korohereza abakurikirana abantu mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya koronavirusi 2019-20, ni ukuvuga kumenya abantu ( abahuye na bo) bashobora kuba barahuye n'umuntu ufite ubwandu.
Imikorere itandukanye yateguwe cyangwa igishyizwe mu bikorwa, hifashishijwe inkunga ya leta mu turere tumwe na tumwe.
