Hari n'izindi nzira zidahutaza cyane, harimo gukoresha ibimenyetso bya Bluetooth mu kwandikisha aho umuntu ari n'izindi telefoni zigendanwa.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ko bagiye gushyiramo mu buryo bwa Android na iOS porogaramu za Bluetooth.
Guverinoma y'Ubushinwa ifatanyije na Alipay, yashyizeho porogaramu muri China, ifasha abaturage kureba niba barigeze guhura n'abantu banduye COVID-19.
Ikoreshwa mu mijyi irenga 200 mu Bushinwa, Singapore yo yahisemo porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether.
Byateguwe n'itsinda ry'abahanga mu by'ikoranabuhanga, byashyizwe ku isoko rusange, kandi bizashyikirizwa leta. Macedonia y'Amajyaruguru yatangije  StopKorona! , porogaramu ya Bluetooth ikurikirana abantu bashobora kuba baranduye kandi ikaganira n'abashinzwe ubuzima vuba.
Porogaramu yakozwe na Minisiteri y'Itumanaho n'Ikoranabuhanga na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Kuva ku ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu yari itegereje kwemezwa na Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, guverinoma yavuze ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abakora imibonano iri mu gihe cy'iterambere ry'ibanze kandi ishobora gushyirwa mu bikorwa mu byumweru bike biri imbere. Porogaramu nk'iyo irateganywa muri Irilande no mu Bufaransa ( StopCovid ).
Australia na Nouvelle Zelande bitegura gushyiraho porogaramu zimeze nka TraceTogether muri Singapour kandi zishingiye kuri porogaramu ya BlueTrace. Uburusiya bushaka gushyiraho porogaramu yo gupima imiterere y'ubutaka ku barwayi basuzumwe COVID-19 kandi batuye i Moscow, kugira ngo bizere ko batava mu ngo zabo.
Umwarimu w'ubwubatsi bw'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, Ross Anderson, yagaragaje ibibazo byinshi bishoboka bijyanye no gukoresha sisitemu zishingiye kuri porogaramu, harimo ibinyoma by'inyungu n'ubushobozi buke bw'imikorere mu gihe igice gito cy'abaturage ari cyo gikoresha porogaramu.
Mu gusubiza impungenge z'ikwirakwizwa rya porogaramu za coronavirus zibeshya cyangwa zangiza, Apple yemereye gusa imiryango yemewe cyangwa yizerwa muri rusange kongera porogaramu zifitanye isano na coronavirus kuri App Store.
Google na Amazon na byo byashyizeho amategeko nk'ayo.
Abashinzwe kubahiriza ubuzima bwite bagaragaje impungenge ku ngaruka za porogaramu za koronavirusi ku igenzura rusange, cyane cyane ku guhagarika ibikorwa remezo by'igenzura byakozwe mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya koronavirusi igihe ibyago bizaba byashize.
Amnesty International n'indi miryango isaga 100 yasohoye itangazo risaba ko hakwiye kubangikanywaho ibyo bikorwa byo kurebera ku mbuga nkoranyambaga.
Ayo mashyirahamwe yashyizeho ibintu umunani agomba kubahiriza mu mishinga ya leta:
igenzura ryagombye kuba rifite amategeko, rikenewe kandi rifite urugero;
kwongera kugenzura no kugenzura byagombye kuba bikubiyemo ingingo zo kureka;
Gukoresha amakuru bigomba gukoreshwa gusa mu rwego rwo kurwanya COVID-19;
umutekano w'amakuru n'ubutumenyekane bigomba kurindwa mu buryo bugaragara;
igenzura rya digitale rigomba kwirinda ko habaho ubwibone n'ubwigunge bw'abantu benshi;
gusangiza amakuru abandi bantu byategetswe n'amategeko;
hakwiye gushyirwaho ingamba zo kwirinda ihohoterwa no kurengera abaturage mu gihe hagize igikorwa cy'ihohoterwa;
 uruhare rw'ingenzi  rw'abashishikajwe bose  bizaba ngombwa, cyane cyane impuguke mu by'ubuzima rusange n'amatsinda y'abantu bari ku ruhande. Ishyirahamwe rya Chaos Computer Club (CCC) na Reporters sans Frontières (Reporter ohne Grenzen) (RSF) mu Budage na byo byasohoye urutonde rw'abantu bahabwa amakuru.
Gahunda yateguwe na Google/Apple igamije gukemura ikibazo cy'igenzura rikomeza mu gukuraho uburyo bwo gukurikirana ikoranabuhanga mu bikoresho byabo igihe bitakiri ngombwa.
Ibihugu bimwe byakoresheje uburyo bwo kumenya aho umuntu aherereye mu gihe cy'imikorere ya porogaramu, ibyo bikaba bikuraho ko umuntu agomba gukurura porogaramu no kwirinda ko yakurikiranwa.
Muri Israel, uburyo bwo gukurikirana imiyoboro y'amazi bwemewe.
Ibisubizo by'imbuga za interineti bifite amakuru y'ibanze yerekeye ahantu umuntu aba ari, bishobora kuba bifite ibibazo bikomeye by'ubuzima bwite.
Ariko, si buri buryo bwose bushingiye kuri seriveri z'ibanze buzakenera kubona amakuru y'ahantu umuntu aba; hari uburyo bumwe bwo gukoresha seriveri z'ibanze mu rwego rwo guhuza abantu gusa, bityo bigatuma habaho ubuzima bwite (reba igice gikurikira).
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, hakoreshejwe uburyo butari kuri porogaramu mu gukurikirana abantu.
Aho gukoresha porogaramu yihariye, iyi porogaramu yakusanyije amakuru yo gukurikirana mu buryo butandukanye, harimo amakuru yo gukurikirana hakoreshejwe ibikoresho bya telefoni n'amadoka, hanyuma bayashyira hamwe kugira ngo bohereze ubutumwa bugufi ku bantu bashobora kuba banduye.
Uretse gukoresha aya makuru mu kuburira abantu bashobora kuba bahuye n'umuntu, guverinoma yashyize amakuru y'aho umuntu ari ku mugaragaro, ibyo bikaba byari byemewe kubera impinduka zikomeye zashyizweho mu mategeko arengera ubuzima bwite bw'amakuru nyuma y'icyorezo cya MERS cyibasiye iki gihugu.
Aya makuru araboneka ku mugaragaro hifashishijwe porogaramu nyinshi na za mbuga za interineti.Ibihugu nka Ubudage byatekereje gukoresha sisitemu yo gucunga ubuzima bwite.
Kugeza ku ya 6 Mata 2020, amakuru y'ibisobanuro byayo ntiyari yaratangwa.
Kurikirana abafite amakuru yihariye ni ihame ryashyizweho neza, rishyigikiwe n'ubushakashatsi bwinshi kuva mu 2013. Ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda y'impuguke arenga 12 yakoraga ku mishinga yihariye, harimo gukoresha ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) kugira ngo bandike aho umuntu ari hafi y'izindi telefoni.
Icyakora, umushinga PEPP-PT ni umuhate wo guhuza uhuza uburyo bwo gukorana bwihariye n'ubw'abantu ku giti cyabo, kandi ntabwo ari porotokore imwe. Porotokore z'abantu ku giti cyabo zirimo porotokore zibumbatiye ku mutekano w'ibanga-zirinda ibyerekeye hafi (DP-PPT/DP-3T), nimero z'itumanaho by'agateganyo (TCN, mbere yitwaga nimero z'ibihe by'itumanaho, CEN), porotokore zifite ibanga ry'ibanga (Privacy Sensitive Protocols) n'imikorere yo gukurikira abantu kuri telefoni (PACT), n'ibindi.
Izi protocole zifasha kwemeza ko amakuru bwite ashobora kumenyekana atava muri icyo gikoresho kandi ko guhuza byose bikorwa kuri icyo gikoresho.
Itsinda ry'Umuryango wa MIT Media Lab ririmo gukora uburyo bwo gukoresha amakuru y'ibanga mu gihe hakusanywa amakuru y'aho umuntu aherereye cyangwa amakuru y'abantu bavugana kugira ngo hakurikiranwe ikwirakwizwa rya COVID-19.
Ubu buryo bushingiye ku byavuye mu gitabo  Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic  cyasohotse muri Werurwe 2020 .
SafeTrace ikoresha ikoranabuhanga rikoresha ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga kugira ngo abantu bashobore gusangiza abandi bantu n'abayobozi amakuru y'aho batuye n'amakuru y'ubuzima, ariko mu buryo budahenze.
Ku ya 5 Mata 2020, TCN Coalition International yashinzwe n'amatsinda yunze ubumwe afite imikorere ihwanye, mu rwego rwo kugabanya amacakubiri no gutuma porogaramu zo gushakisha no gutanga amakuru ku isi zikorana neza, ari na byo by'ingenzi mu gutuma zikoreshwa n'abantu benshi.
Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, guverinoma ya Singapore yatangaje ko yashyize ahagaragara kode y'isoko ya BlueTrace ikoreshwa na porogaramu yayo yemewe.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple, bigenga porogaramu za Android na iOS, batangaje ko bashyizeho gahunda yo gukurikirana abakorana nabo, bavuga ko bizatuma ubuzima bwite bw'abantu burushaho kubumburwa kandi ko bizakoresha ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth Low Energy hamwe na cryptography itanga ubuzima bwite.
Batanze kandi ibisobanuro by'ibanze by'ikoranabuhanga ryifashishwa muri iyo gahunda.
Apple na Google bavuga ko iyi gahunda izashyirwa mu bikorwa mu byiciro bitatu:
gushyiraho ibikoresho bifasha leta gukora porogaramu z'ubutegetsi zo gukurikirana coronavirus mu buryo bubahiriza ubuzima bwite
Google na Apple biteganya gukemura ibibazo by'ikoreshwa ry'iki cyemezo no gukomeza gukurikiranwa binyuze mu kubanza gukwirakwizwa hakoreshejwe amavugurura ya sisitemu y'imikorere no kuyakuraho mu buryo nk'ubwo nyuma y'uko iterabwoba rirangiye.
Guhindura imiterere y'umuti (nanone bita guhindura icyerekezo, gusubiramo, guhindura imiterere cyangwa guhindura icyerekezo cy'umuti) bisobanura guhindura umuti wemewe ku bw'indwara cyangwa indwara itandukanye n'iyo wateguwe mbere.
Ni icyiciro cy'ubushakashatsi mu bya siyansi kiri gukorwa kugira ngo hakorwe imiti ikora neza kandi itariyobya COVID-19.
Ibindi bikorwa by'ubushakashatsi harimo gukora urukingo rwa COVID-19 no gutera amaraso y'abantu bakize. SARS-CoV-2 ifite poroteyine zigera kuri 66 zo kuvura, buri poroteyine ikaba ifite ahantu henshi ishobora gufatira ibintu.
Isesengura ry'ibi bice by'ubuhuza ritanga igishushanyo mbonera cy'uburyo bwo gukora imiti yica virusi ikora neza mu kurwanya poroteyine za COVID-19.
Amwe mu ma poroteyine y'ingenzi SARS-CoV-2 yibasira harimo poroteyine y'ubwoko bwa papaine, poroteyine y'ubwoko bwa RNA polymerase, poroteyine ya helicase, poroteyine ya S na poroteyine ya ADP ribose phosphatase.
Hussein A, et al. bakoze ubushakashatsi ku miti myinshi y'abahatanira ikamba, hanyuma bayikoresha neza kandi bayisuzuma kugira ngo barebe niba ihwanye n'imiti yemewe ikoreshwa mu kwihutisha iterambere ry'umuti ukomeye wa SARS-CoV-2 mu bushakashatsi bwabo mbere y'ubushakashatsi kugira ngo bajye batanga inama mu gukora ubushakashatsi bw'ubuvuzi.
Chloroquine ni umuti uvura malariya ukoreshwa no mu ndwara zimwe na zimwe ziterwa n'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kurwanya indwara.
Ku ya 18 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine bifitanye isano ari mu miti ine iri gukorwaho igerageza ry'ubuvuzi rya Solidarity.
Guverineri wa New York, Andrew Cuomo, yatangaje ko igerageza rya leta ya New York kuri chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine rizatangira ku ya 24 Werurwe. Ku ya 28 Werurwe, FDA yemeje ikoreshwa rya hydroxychloroquine sulfate na chloroquine phosphate hakurikijwe icyemezo cy'ikoreshwa mu buryo bwihutirwa (EUA).
Uyu muti ntabwo wemejwe n'ikigo cya FDA mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi kandi wemewe n'amategeko ya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gusa nk'umuti w'ubushakashatsi mu kwihutisha ku barwayi bari mu bitaro ariko badashobora kuvurwa mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi.
CDC yavuze ko "ikoreshwa, ingano y'imiti cyangwa igihe cy'imiti ya hydroxychloroquine mu kwirinda cyangwa kuvura ubwandu bwa SARS-COV-2" bitaremezwa.
