Urukingo rwa COVID-19 ni urukingo rw'ibanze rw'indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Nubwo nta rukingo na rumwe rwarangije igerageza, hari byinshi bigerageza gukorwa.
Mu mpera za Gashyantare 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryavuze ko nta rukingo rw'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2, virusi itera iyi ndwara, rutegerejwe nibura mu gihe cy'amezi 18.
Muri Mata, hari inkingo eshanu z'abakandida zari ziri mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubushakashatsi ku mutekano.
COVID-19 yagaragaye mu Kuboza 2019.
Icyorezo gikomeye cyibasiye isi yose mu mwaka wa 2020, bituma hashorwa amafaranga menshi kandi hakorwa ubushakashatsi kugira ngo havumburwe urukingo.
Imiryango myinshi irimo ikoresha ingano z'ibinyabuzima byasohotse mu gukora inkingo zishobora gukingira SARS-CoV-2.
Muri Mata, CEPI yagaragaje ko ibyo umuntu agomba gukora kugira ngo hakorwe urukingo ari umuvuduko, ubushobozi bwo gukora, gukwirakwiza ku rwego runini no kugera ku isi hose.
Muri Mata, abahanga mu bya siyansi bo muri CEPI batangaje ko hari ibigo 10 by'ikoranabuhanga bitandukanye biri gukora ubushakashatsi no gukora porogaramu mu ntangiriro za 2020 hagamijwe gukora urukingo rukora neza rw'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Ibipimo by'ibanze by'umwanya wa mbere w'uburinzi byakozweho ubushakashatsi harimo:
nucleic acid (DNA na RNA) (ikoreshwa mu cyiciro cya mbere cy' ikorwa ry' urukingo rw' ikompanyi y' ubwizigamire: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
virusi (Igice cya I: Umuvugizi w'urukingo wa CanSino Biologics, virusi ya adenovirus yo mu bwoko bwa 5)
Nk'uko abahanga mu bya siyansi bo muri CEPI babivuze muri Mata, inkingo 115 z'inkingo ziri mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'iterambere, 78 muri zo (79 zitangwa na Milken) zemejwe ko zikora, n'izindi 37 zatangajwe, ariko amakuru y'ibanze yatanzwe ari make (bivugwa ko ziri gutegurwa cyangwa zitegurwa).
Icyiciro cya mbere n'icya kabiri cy'igerageza, ni igerageza ry'ibanze ry'ubuziranenge n'ububasha bw'umubiri, ubusanzwe rigenzurwa ku buryo butandukanye, rigenzurwa hifashishijwe imiti ya placebo, rikorerwa mu bigo byinshi, rigamije kumenya neza uko ingero z'indwara zikoreshwa zingana.
Ubusanzwe igerageza ryo mu cyiciro cya III rigira abantu benshi, harimo n'itsinda ry'abapimisha, rigamije kureba niba urukingo rwafasha mu kurinda indwara, ariko kandi rugakomeza gukurikirana ingaruka mbi iyo rukoreshejwe mu rugero rwiza.
Mu nkingo 79 zatangiye gukorwa (zemejwe mu ntangiriro za Mata 2020), 74 zari zitaragera mu cyiciro cy'igerageza ku bantu (zikiri mu bushakashatsi bw'ibanze).
