Abashinzwe ubuzima mu Bushinwa no muri Koreya batanga inama yo gukoresha chloroquine.
Ariko, Ikigo cya Wuhan gishinzwe iby'iby'indwara z'ibyorezo, nubwo cyatanga inama yo gukoresha grame imwe ku munsi, kivuga ko kongeraho kabiri iyo miti biba ari bibi cyane kandi bishobora kwica.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yemeje ikoreshwa rya hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine mu buryo bw'ubuyobozi bwo gukoresha mu buryo bwihutirwa ku bushake bw'abaganga bavura abarwayi ba COVID-19. Amabwiriza yo mu Bushinwa yo mu cyiciro cya 7 harimo n'amaraso ya interferon, ribavirin na lumifenovir yo kurwanya COVID-19.
Amakuru y'ibanze agaragaza ko hakenewe imiti myinshi ya ribavirine kugira ngo SARS-CoV-2 ihagarikwe mu bushakashatsi bwa in vitro.
Nitazoxanide yagiriwe inama yo gukoreshwa mu isuzuma rikomeje mu mubiri w'umuntu, nyuma yo kugaragaza ko igabanya ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 mu rugero ruto.
Ubushakashatsi ku miti ya chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine ikoreshwa cyangwa idafite azithromycin ifite aho ihuriye n'indi, byatumye abaganga batemera iyi miti nta bushakashatsi bw'inyongera. Oseltamivir ntibuza SARS-CoV-2 mu mubiri kandi nta ruhare ruzwi igira mu kuvura COVID-19.
Igitutu cy'imikorere y'ingirabuzima fatizo gishobora kuba ikibazo cy'ingorane mu bihe bikomeye bya COVID-19.
Hari ibimenyetso byerekana ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira ubushobozi bwo kurwanya igitutu cya cytokine. Tocilizumab yashyizwe mu mabwiriza y'ubuvuzi na komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima yo mu Bushinwa nyuma y'ubushakashatsi buciriritse bwakorewe.
Ubu iri mu igeragezwa ry'icyiciro cya 2 mu gihugu cyose cy'Ubutaliyani nyuma yo kugaragaza ko ifite ingaruka nziza ku bantu barwaye cyane.
Ugizwe n'ikizamini cy'amaraso cya serumu y'uburozi kugira ngo hamenyekane ko hari umuntu ufite ikibazo cy'indwara ya sitokine, kigomba kurwanya izo ndwara abantu bakeka ko ari zo zishe bamwe muri abo bantu.
L antagonist ya interleukin-6 receptor yemejwe na FDA hashingiwe ku bushakashatsi bw'ibisobanuro by'ibyabaye mu gihe cy'ubuvuzi mu kuvura indwara ya SRS-RSS ifata indwara itandukanye n'iy'izindi, kuvurwa na CAR T cells, mu 2017.
Kugeza ubu nta kimenyetso na kimwe gifatika kigaragaza ko tocilizumab ifasha mu kuvura CRS.
Guhererekanya abasirikare b'umubiri b'ingenzi kandi batunganyijwe, bakorwa n'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bw'abantu bakize COVID-19 ku bantu babukeneye, biri gukorwaho ubushakashatsi nk'uburyo bwo kwirinda indwara butari ubw'inkingo.
Iyi nzira yagezweho mu kurwanya SARS ariko nta musaruro ufatika yabonye.
Gukuramo virusi ni uburyo bw'ibikorwa bwitezwe ko bushobora gutuma umuntu arinda SARS-CoV-2 akoresheje imiti y'ubwirinzi.
Ariko kandi, ubundi buryo butandukanye, urugero nka cytotoxicity ishingiye kuri za anticorps, cyangwa phagocytosis, bushobora kuba bushoboka.
Ubundi buryo bwo gukoresha imiti igabanya ubukana, urugero nko gukoresha abasirikare b'umubiri b'ubwoko bumwe, burimo burategurwa.
Umusaruro w'umusemburo w'abantu bakize, ugizwe n'igice cy'amaraso y'abarwayi bakize kandi kirimo udukoko dutera iyo virusi, ushobora kongerwa kugira ngo ikwirakwizwa ry'iyi virusi byitwe vuba.
Indwara za koronavirusi, itsinda ry'indwara zifitanye isano ya bugufi
Li Wenliang, umuganga mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan, yaje kwandura COVID-19 nyuma aza gupfa nyuma yo kugaragaza ko iyi virusi ikwirakwizwa.
